英文内容: high-quality font with excellent readability and visual appeal. Suitable for various design applications including print, digital, and branding projects. Enhances design communication through clear typographic expression.

Form-fitting jeans that hug the body tightly from waist to ankle, made of stretchy denim (blended with spandex or elastane) for flexibility and comfort. They have a low, mid, or high waist and often include classic jeans details (pockets, rivets) and a zipper/button closure. Available in various washes (from light to black). Suitable for casual outings, dates, or street style—paired with oversized tops (hoodies, sweaters), tucked-in shirts, or leather jackets to balance the tight fit.

Cropped pants that end between the knee and ankle (typically mid-calf), offering a lightweight option for warm weather. Made of fabrics like cotton, linen, denim, or stretch blends, they can have a straight, slim, or wide leg. They often have a button/zipper closure or elastic waistband. Suitable for spring and summer—casual outings, shopping, or garden parties—paired with sandals, flats, or sneakers and tops like t-shirts, tank tops, or lightweight blouses.

A classic pair of jeans with a straight silhouette—legs maintain a consistent width from hip to ankle (no tapering or flaring). Made of durable denim fabric (light, medium, or dark wash), they often have traditional jeans details like rivets, front pockets, back pockets, and a zipper/button closure. Suitable for all body types, pairing well with t-shirts, shirts, sweaters, or jackets. Ideal for casual outings, office work (relaxed dress codes), or everyday wear.

Jeans combining the durability of denim with the functionality of cargo pants, featuring multiple large patch pockets (on the thighs, hips, or back) with button or zipper closures. They have a relaxed fit for ease of movement, made of heavy-duty denim (medium to dark wash). They typically have a straight or slightly tapered leg and a zipper/button closure. Suitable for casual, rugged looks—outdoor activities, gardening, or weekend errands—paired with t-shirts, flannel shirts, or work boots.

Jeans with a waistline that sits below the natural waist (usually 1-2 inches below the belly button), creating a casual, retro vibe. They can have various leg styles (straight, skinny, flared) and are made of denim (various washes). They typically have a zipper/button closure, belt loops, and classic jeans pockets. Suitable for casual outings, street style, or summer days—paired with cropped tops, untucked t-shirts, or tank tops to avoid covering the low waist.

Casual pants with a straight, non-tapered leg (width remains consistent from hip to ankle), offering a classic, versatile fit. Made of soft, breathable fabrics like cotton, linen, or twill, they come in neutral colors (beige, gray, navy) or light pastels. Features may include a button/zipper closure, belt loops, and front/back pockets. Suitable for a range of casual to semi-formal occasions—office work (relaxed dress codes), brunch, or weekend trips—paired with shirts, sweaters, or blazers.

Casual, comfortable pants designed for loungewear or light physical activity, featuring a relaxed fit through the hips and thighs and tapered, cuffed legs. Made of soft fabrics like cotton jersey, fleece, or French terry, they have an elastic waistband with a drawstring, side pockets, and sometimes back pockets. They often have a slightly baggy fit for comfort. Suitable for lazy weekends, post-gym wear, or running errands—paired with hoodies, t-shirts, or sneakers.

Athletic pants designed for physical activity or casual wear, featuring a slim fit through the thighs and tapered legs that end in cuffed ankles (elastic cuffs to keep the pants in place). Made of stretchy, moisture-wicking fabrics like polyester, spandex blends, or cotton jersey, they often have an elastic waistband with a drawstring for adjustability and side pockets. Suitable for gym workouts, running, yoga, or loungewear—paired with athletic t-shirts, hoodies, or sneakers.

Casual pants with a slim (but not tight) fit—closely hugging the hips and thighs while tapering slightly toward the ankles. Made of lightweight, comfortable fabrics like cotton, cotton blends, or linen, they come in solid colors (black, gray, khaki) or subtle patterns. Features may include an elastic waistband, drawstring, or button closure, and side/back pockets. Suitable for casual occasions like weekends, brunch dates, or casual office environments—paired with polo shirts, t-shirts, or lightweight sweaters.

Casual pants with legs that flare gently from the knees to the ankles (similar to flared jeans but made of non-denim fabrics), offering a relaxed, stylish fit. Crafted from lightweight fabrics like cotton, linen, or rayon, they often have a mid or high waist and a button/zipper closure or elastic waistband. They come in solid colors or patterns (florals, stripes). Suitable for spring and summer—casual outings, brunch, or beach trips—paired with fitted tops (tank tops, tucked-in blouses) to balance the flare.

Versatile pants made of khaki-colored twill fabric (though now available in other neutral colors like beige, navy, or gray), featuring a straight or slim fit. They are lightweight and breathable, with a button/zipper closure, belt loops, and front/back pockets. They can be casual or semi-formal depending on the fabric and styling. Suitable for office work (relaxed dress codes), brunch, or weekend trips—paired with shirts, sweaters, or blazers for a polished look.

Loose-fitting pants with a dropped crotch (low-slung crotch) and tapered legs that narrow toward the ankles, creating a baggy, comfortable silhouette. Made of soft, flowy fabrics like cotton, rayon, or linen, they often have an elastic waistband and side pockets. They come in solid colors, patterns (stripes, florals), or prints. Suitable for casual wear—loungewear, beach cover-ups, or weekend outings—paired with fitted tops (crop tops, tank tops) to avoid a shapeless look.

Comfortable pants made of soft, stretchy knitted fabrics like cotton, acrylic, or cashmere blends, offering a cozy, relaxed fit. They can have a straight, wide, or tapered leg and often feature an elastic waistband for comfort. They come in solid colors, stripes, or subtle patterns. Suitable for loungewear, casual outings (in cooler weather), or winter days—paired with knitted sweaters, hoodies, or oversized t-shirts and boots or slippers.

Jeans with wide, flowing legs that flare significantly from the hips or thighs to the ankles, creating a dramatic, relaxed silhouette. Crafted from denim (various washes), they often have a high waist to balance the wide legs and prevent the fit from looking overwhelming. They may include classic jeans details (pockets, rivets) and a zipper/button closure. Suitable for casual outings, street style looks, or summer days—paired with fitted tops (tank tops, tucked-in t-shirts) to highlight the waist.

Jeans with legs that flare slightly from the knees to the ankles (less dramatic than wide-leg jeans), creating a retro, timeless silhouette. Crafted from denim (various washes), they may have a mid or high waist and classic jeans details (pockets, rivets). They can be slim-fitting through the thighs to emphasize the flare or have a relaxed fit. Suitable for casual outings, retro-inspired looks, or date nights—paired with tucked-in shirts, crop tops, or platform shoes to elongate the legs.

Athletic pants designed for cold weather, featuring a soft fleece lining inside to provide extra warmth. The outer layer is made of durable, stretchy fabrics like polyester or spandex blends (often moisture-wicking for activity), and they have a slim or relaxed fit with tapered, cuffed legs. They include an elastic waistband with a drawstring and side pockets. Suitable for winter workouts, outdoor activities (hiking, running), or loungewear—paired with hoodies, thermal tops, or sneakers.

Jeans with a waistline that sits significantly above the natural waist (usually 2-3 inches above the belly button), designed to elongate the legs and highlight the waist. They can have various leg styles (straight, skinny, wide-leg, flared) and are made of denim (various washes). They typically have a zipper/button closure, belt loops, and classic jeans pockets. Suitable for all body types—casual outings, dates, or street style—paired with cropped tops, tucked-in t-shirts, or bodysuits to showcase the high waist.

Formal pants designed to be worn with suits, blazers, or dress shirts, featuring a tailored, slim or straight fit. Made of smooth, structured fabrics like wool, polyester blends, or cotton twill, they have a flat front or pleated front, a button/zipper closure, belt loops, and side/back pockets (often with hidden closures for a sleek look). They typically have a straight or slightly tapered leg. Suitable for business meetings, formal events, weddings, or office work—paired with dress shirts, blazers, and dress shoes.

A one-piece garment with short sleeves (typically hitting at or above the elbow) and a connected pair of trousers (slim, straight, or wide-leg). It can have various necklines (crewneck, V-neck, collared) and closures (zipper, buttons). Made of lightweight fabrics like cotton, linen, or rayon, it’s ideal for warm weather (spring, summer) and casual settings like brunch, beach outings, or outdoor concerts.

A versatile dress designed to mimic the style of a button-down shirt, featuring a collar, front button placket (from neck to hem), and often a slightly structured fit. It may have long, short, or rolled-up sleeves, and can be belted at the waist for a more defined silhouette. Suitable for both casual (paired with sneakers) and semi-formal (paired with heels) occasions, such as office work, weekend outings, or brunch dates.

A dress that hits between the knee and ankle (typically mid-calf), offering a versatile length that flatters most heights. It can come in various styles (A-line, sheath, wrap, shirt dress) and sleeve options, and is suitable for all seasons—lightweight fabrics (linen, cotton) for summer, and heavier fabrics (knit, velvet) for winter. Perfect for casual outings, office work, or semi-formal events like cocktail parties, paired with flats, boots, or heels.

A dress made of denim fabric (light, medium, or dark wash), combining the casual vibe of jeans with the femininity of a dress. Styles include shirt dresses (with collars and buttons), fit-and-flare, or wrap designs, with lengths ranging from mini to midi. It may have details like rivets, pockets, or distressed patches (for a vintage look). Suitable for casual occasions like weekend trips, picnics, or shopping, paired with sneakers, sandals, or ankle boots.

A dress without shoulder straps, designed to stay in place by fitting snugly around the bust (often with built-in boning or elastic for support). It can have a sweetheart neckline, straight neckline, or off-the-shoulder variation, and silhouettes range from fitted (mermaid, sheath) to flowy (A-line). Suitable for formal or semi-formal events like weddings, proms, or cocktail parties, paired with statement jewelry and heels.

A sophisticated one-piece garment that combines the structure of a blazer with trousers, featuring a collared neckline, front buttons (like a blazer), and a tailored fit. The bodice mimics a blazer (with lapels and often padded shoulders), and the trousers are usually straight or wide-leg for a formal look. Made of structured fabrics like wool, crepe, or polyester, it’s ideal for formal events, business meetings, or office work—paired with heels for a polished finish.

A one-piece garment where the waistline sits above the natural waist (usually 2-3 inches above the belly button), creating the illusion of longer legs. The bodice is short, and the trousers are often high-waisted with a wide or straight leg. It may have a zipper closure at the back or front, and can be sleeveless, short-sleeved, or long-sleeved. Suitable for various occasions—casual (paired with sneakers) or semi-formal (paired with heels)—depending on the fabric and design.

A sleek, minimalist dress with thin shoulder straps (spaghetti straps) and a form-fitting or slightly flowy silhouette, typically made of lightweight, smooth fabrics like silk, satin, or rayon. It often has a V-neck or scoop neck and hits at mid-thigh to midi length. Originally designed as undergarments, modern slip dresses are worn as outerwear—ideal for summer evenings, parties, or romantic dates (can be layered with a jacket for cooler weather).

A functional one-piece garment designed for physical activity (e.g., yoga, running, gym workouts) or casual loungewear. It’s made of stretchy, moisture-wicking fabrics (spandex, polyester blends) with a slim or relaxed fit, and may have features like a high neck, racerback, or elastic waistband for comfort and mobility. Suitable for workouts, post-gym errands, or lazy weekends at home—paired with sneakers or slides.

A one-piece garment consisting of trousers with attached shoulder straps (braces) that fasten at the front or back. They can be made of denim (classic style), cotton, or corduroy, with a loose or slim fit. Overalls often have multiple pockets (front, back, or side) for functionality. Suitable for casual settings like weekends, gardening, or outings with friends, paired with t-shirts, tank tops, or sweaters (for colder seasons).

A dress designed to cinch tightly at the waist (either with a built-in elastic band, a drawstring, or a tailored seam) to highlight the waistline, with a bodice and skirt that flare slightly or flow outward. Silhouettes like A-line, fit-and-flare, or wrap dresses often fall into this category. It flatters most body types, suitable for both casual (paired with flats) and semi-formal (paired with heels) events, such as dates, parties, or office gatherings.

A dress made of real or faux leather, offering a bold, edgy look. It can be form-fitting (sheath, bodycon) or slightly loose, with styles like mini, midi, or shirt dresses (with collars and buttons). Details may include zippers, studs, or belted waists. Suitable for evening events, parties, or a trendy night out—paired with ankle boots or heels. Faux leather versions are more affordable and animal-friendly, while real leather offers durability.

A dress that extends to the ankle or floor, with a flowy or fitted silhouette. It can have various sleeve styles (sleeveless, short-sleeved, long-sleeved) and necklines, and is often made of lightweight fabrics (chiffon, linen, cotton) for summer, or heavier fabrics (velvet, wool) for winter. Suitable for a range of occasions—from casual beach days (paired with sandals) to formal events (paired with heels and a shawl), depending on the fabric and design.

A dress featuring small or large floral patterns (realistic or abstract) on a solid background (light or dark). It can come in various styles—shirt dress, fit-and-flare, wrap, or slip—and lengths (mini to maxi). Fabrics range from lightweight cotton (summer) to knitted wool (winter). The floral print adds a feminine, playful touch, making it suitable for spring and summer outings, garden parties, or casual dates.

A dress featuring horizontal, vertical, or diagonal stripes (thick or thin, colorful or monochrome) on a solid background. It can come in various styles (shirt dress, fit-and-flare, slip) and lengths (mini to maxi). Vertical stripes create a slimming effect, while horizontal stripes add a playful touch. Made of fabrics like cotton, linen, or knit, it’s suitable for casual outings, office work (with a blazer), or weekend trips—paired with neutral shoes to let the stripes stand out.

A functional, utilitarian one-piece garment inspired by workwear, featuring wide-leg trousers, multiple large patch pockets (on the thighs, hips, or back), and a front zipper or button closure. It’s usually made of durable fabrics like cotton twill or canvas, with a relaxed fit for ease of movement. Often paired with boots or sneakers, it’s ideal for outdoor activities, casual errands, or a trendy, edgy everyday look.

A one-piece garment without sleeves (armholes cut high or low) and connected trousers, offering a cool, minimalist look for warm weather. It may have a V-neck, scoop neck, or halter neck, and trousers can be slim, straight, or wide-leg. Made of fabrics like linen, silk, or cotton, it’s perfect for summer parties, outdoor weddings, or casual outings (paired with a cardigan for cooler evenings).

A dress crafted from knitted fabrics (e.g., wool, cotton, acrylic, or cashmere), offering warmth and a soft, stretchy texture. It can range from form-fitting to oversized, with styles like turtlenecks, crewnecks, or off-the-shoulder designs. Lengths vary (mini to maxi), and it may have ribbed details or cable-knit patterns. Perfect for transitional seasons (spring, fall) or winter (layered with coats), suitable for casual outings, office work (with a blazer), or cozy evenings at home.

A one-piece garment with a relaxed, oversized fit (both bodice and trousers), prioritizing comfort without sacrificing style. It may have a drop waist, wide legs, or a slouchy bodice, and is made of soft, lightweight fabrics like cotton, linen, or rayon. Suitable for casual settings like weekends, loungewear, or beach outings—paired with sneakers, sandals, or flip-flops for a laid-back vibe.

A one-piece garment with wide, flowing legs that flare from the waist or hips, creating a dramatic, elegant silhouette. It typically has a fitted bodice (with a V-neck, crewneck, or collared design) to balance the wide legs, and may feature a zipper or button closure. Made of fabrics like linen, crepe, or cotton, it’s perfect for summer events, beach weddings, or office work (with a blazer), as it’s both stylish and comfortable.

内容: 刺激的游乐园风格。一个大区域内充满了色彩缤纷的游乐设施，如过山车、摩天轮和旋转木马。空气中充满了兴奋的尖叫声和游戏音乐。人们排队等候游乐设施，还有摊位在卖爆米花、棉花糖和其他美食。
英文内容: thrilling amusement park style . A large area filled with colorful rides, such as roller coasters, Ferris wheels, and carousels. The sound of screams of excitement and music from the games fills the air. People are lined up for rides, and there are stalls selling popcorn, cotton candy, and other treats

内容: 中式茶室风格。深色木材，传统的中式家具，如低矮的茶桌和配套的椅子。丝绸或竹子印刷的织物用于窗帘和靠垫。一套传统的中式茶具被显著展示。房间墙上可能有书法或绘画作品，以及柔和、暖色调的照明来创造宁静的氛围。
英文内容: Chinese - style tea room style . Dark - wood, traditional Chinese - style furniture, such as a low - slung tea table and matching chairs. Silk or bamboo - printed fabrics are used for curtains and cushions. A set of traditional Chinese tea - making utensils is prominently displayed. The room may have a calligraphy or painting on the wall, and a soft, warm - toned lighting to create a serene atmosphere

内容: 斯堪的纳维亚风格厨房。浅色木质橱柜，通常是白色或浅灰色。不锈钢电器与干净现代的外观融为一体。开放式布局，中央岛台用于食物准备和社交。几何形状简单的吊灯提供工作照明。房间充满自然光，可能还有几个盆栽植物增添绿色
英文内容: Scandinavian - style kitchen style . Light - colored wooden cabinets, often white or light gray. Stainless - steel appliances blend in with the clean, modern look. A large, open - plan layout with a central island for food preparation and socializing. Pendant lights with simple, geometric shapes provide task lighting. The room is filled with natural light, and there may be a few potted plants for a touch of greenery

内容: 被雪覆盖的山峰风格。雄伟的雪山，在阳光下闪耀着光芒的斜坡。雪是纯净的白色，可能有冰川从山坡上流下来。空气寒冷而清新，从山脚或附近有利的观察点看去，景色令人叹为观止。
英文内容: snow - covered mountain peaks style . Majestic, snow - capped mountains with slopes glistening in the sunlight. The snow is pure white, and there may be glaciers flowing down the mountainsides. The air is cold and crisp, and the view from the base or a nearby vantage point is breathtaking

内容: 神秘沼泽湿地风格。湿地区域充满死水、高高的芦苇和根部淹没在水中的柏树。水色黑暗浑浊，有漂浮的植被。沼泽上常有雾气缭绕，能听到青蛙的叫声和奇异鸟类的啼鸣
英文内容: mysterious swamp wetland style . A wetland area filled with stagnant water, tall reeds, and cypress trees with their roots submerged. The water is dark and murky, and there are patches of floating vegetation. Fog often hovers over the swamp, and the croaking of frogs and calls of strange birds can be heard

内容: 历史悠久的古镇巷弄风格。狭窄、蜿蜒的小巷，铺有石板的地面。老式房屋排列在小巷两侧，配有木制门窗。有售卖传统手工艺品和当地特产的小店。墙壁上爬满了常春藤，空气中弥漫着历史感和怀旧情绪。
英文内容: historic ancient town alleys style . Narrow, winding alleys with stone - paved floors. Old - fashioned houses with wooden doors and windows line the alleys. There are small shops selling traditional handicrafts and local specialties. The walls are covered in ivy, and the atmosphere is filled with a sense of history and nostalgia

内容: 日式禅宗风格客厅。榻榻米覆盖地面，有低矮的沙发或坐垫。设计简单，不杂乱，注重自然材料如木头、竹子和纸。小而精心安排的花艺或盆景树增添了一抹自然气息。光线柔和，散射，营造出宁静祥和的环境
英文内容: Japanese zen living room style . Tatami mats cover the floor, and there are low - lying sofas or floor cushions. A simple, uncluttered design with a focus on natural materials like wood, bamboo, and paper. A small, carefully arranged flower arrangement or a bonsai tree adds a touch of nature. The lighting is soft and diffused, creating a peaceful and calming environment

内容: 现代极简主义客厅风格。干净、不杂乱的空间，家具简单几何形状。中性色系如白色、黑色和灰色。地板通常是光滑的，大窗户让充足的自然光进入。装饰元素极少，注重功能性。
英文内容: modern minimalist living room style . Clean, uncluttered space with simple, geometric - shaped furniture. Neutral color palette like white, black, and gray. Floors are often smooth, and large windows let in plenty of natural light. A minimal number of decorative elements, with a focus on functionality

内容: 神奇的奇幻花园风格。一个花园里充满了奇异多彩的植物，它们在阳光下似乎会发光。有小精灵般的生物在飞舞，蘑菇大得像房子一样。一条蜿蜒的小径穿过花园，隐藏的角落和缝隙里充满了神奇的宝藏。
英文内容: magical wonderland garden style . A garden filled with strange, colorful plants that seem to glow in the sunlight. There are small, fairy - like creatures flitting about, and mushrooms as big as houses. A small, winding path leads through the garden, and there are hidden nooks and crannies filled with magical treasures

内容: 宁静的乡村田野风格。广阔的麦田或玉米田在风中轻轻摇曳。远处矗立着老式农舍和红色谷仓。土路蜿蜒穿过田野，附近有一条小溪蜿蜒流过。奶牛或绵羊在木栅栏围着的牧场上吃草
英文内容: peaceful rural fields style . Vast fields of wheat or corn gently rustling in the wind. Old - fashioned farmhouses with red - painted barns stand in the distance. Dirt roads wind through the fields, and a small stream meanders nearby. Cows or sheep graze in pastures surrounded by wooden fences

内容: 繁荣的夜市街道风格。街道上摆满了明亮的摊位，售卖美味的街头美食、独特的纪念品和手工艺品。空气中弥漫着烹饪食物的香味，音乐和笑声此起彼伏。人们在熙熙攘攘中享受着充满活力的氛围，头顶上挂着五彩缤纷的灯笼。
英文内容: prosperous night market streets style . Streets filled with brightly - lit stalls selling delicious street food, unique trinkets, and souvenirs. The air is filled with the smell of food cooking and the sounds of music and laughter. People are bustling around, enjoying the vibrant atmosphere, and there are colorful lanterns hanging overhead

内容: 阳光明媚的海滩海滨风格。广阔的金色沙滩，清澈碧蓝的海水轻轻拍打着岸边。棕榈树在风中摇曳，提供着阴凉。海滩游客躺在色彩鲜艳的毛巾上，岸边点缀着各式各样的遮阳伞。天空湛蓝，白云蓬松
英文内容: sunny beach seaside style . Expansive stretches of golden sand, with clear blue ocean waters gently rolling in. Palm trees swaying in the breeze, providing shade. Beachgoers relax on colorful towels, and there are umbrellas dotting the shore. The sky is bright blue with fluffy white clouds

内容: 创意工作室风格。开放式空间，高天花板和大窗户以引入自然光。墙壁上挂有色彩丰富、令人振奋的艺术作品。一个大型、看起来杂乱无章的工作桌，上面摆满了艺术用品、工具和未完成的项目。舒适的椅子和沙发，看起来既古怪又适合头脑风暴。串灯或工业风格的吊灯为照明增添了一丝创意。
英文内容: creative studio style . Open - plan space with high ceilings and large windows for natural light. Colorful, inspiring artwork on the walls. A large, messy - looking worktable filled with art supplies, tools, and half - finished projects. Comfortable, yet eclectic - looking chairs and sofas for brainstorming sessions. String lights or industrial - style pendant lights add a touch of creativity to the lighting

内容: 繁忙的城市街道风格。人行道上挤满了匆匆行走的人群。高楼大厦沿街而立，玻璃幕墙反射着城市灯光。公交车、汽车和出租车匆匆驶过，霓虹灯闪烁的商店、咖啡馆和餐馆数不胜数
英文内容: bustling city streets style . Crowded sidewalks filled with people walking in a hurry. Tall skyscrapers line the streets, with glass facades reflecting the city lights. Buses, cars, and taxis rush by, and there are numerous shops, cafes, and restaurants with neon signs glowing

内容: 复古城镇广场风格。一个广场，四周是像装饰艺术或维多利亚风格这样的复古建筑。老式的路灯照亮了这个区域，人们坐在长椅上聊天。中心的音乐台可能会举办现场音乐活动，周围停放着经典汽车。
英文内容: retro town square style . A square with buildings in a vintage style, such as Art Deco or Victorian. Old - fashioned streetlights illuminate the area, and there are benches where people sit and chat. A bandstand in the center may host live music events, and classic cars are parked around the square

内容: 豪华酒店套房风格。舒适的高品质地毯，大而舒适的床铺，床上用品为高纱线密度。看起来昂贵的家具，通常配以优雅的装饰。独立的客厅配有平板电视和装满高档饮品的迷你吧。浴室有大理石台面和高端装置。枝形吊灯和壁灯提供温馨豪华的光芒。
英文内容: luxury hotel suite style . Plush, high - quality carpets, and large, comfortable beds with high - thread - count sheets. Expensive - looking furniture, often with elegant upholstery. A separate living area with a flat - screen TV and a mini - bar stocked with premium drinks. The bathroom has marble countertops and high - end fixtures. Chandeliers and wall sconces provide a warm, luxurious glow

内容: 童话小镇街道风格。鹅卵石街道两旁排列着色彩斑斓的小房子，屋顶覆盖着茅草。每栋房子前都有鲜花盛开的花园，还有售卖手工艺品和糖果的小店。一座小石桥横跨穿过小镇的小溪，孩子们在街上玩耍
英文内容: fairy - tale town streets style . Cobblestone streets lined with colorful, small houses with thatched roofs. Flower - filled gardens in front of each house, and small shops selling handicrafts and sweets. A small, stone bridge crosses a stream running through the town, and children play in the streets

内容: 未来科技城风格。城市景观充满了流线型、充满未来感的先进建筑。空中飞驰着飞行汽车，到处都是巨大的发光全息广告牌。这座城市由清洁能源供电，随处可见太阳能电池板和风力涡轮机。有悬浮步道和先进的交通枢纽
英文内容: future - tech city style . A cityscape filled with sleek, futuristic buildings with advanced architecture. Flying cars zip through the air, and large, glowing holographic billboards are everywhere. The city is powered by clean energy, with solar panels and wind turbines visible. There are floating walkways and advanced transportation hubs

内容: 经典欧洲书房风格。墙壁上的深色木镶板，装饰有精美的、细节丰富的书架，摆满了皮革装帧的书籍。装饰繁复的古董风格书桌和椅子，通常带有雕刻的木工。枝形吊灯或古董风格的灯具提供温暖柔和的光线。使用如酒红色和森林绿等丰富、深邃的色彩。
英文内容: classic European study style . Dark - wood paneling on the walls, with elegant, detailed bookshelves filled with leather - bound books. Ornate, antique - style desks and chairs, often with carved woodwork. Chandeliers or antique - looking lamps provide warm, soft lighting. Rich, deep colors like burgundy and forest green are used

内容: 古城堡庭院风格。一座大型石头铺就的庭院位于古城堡的墙内。石头经过风化，显露出岁月的痕迹。有小而精致的花园，种植着色彩斑斓的花朵和灌木。中心可能有一个喷泉在喷水，鸟鸣声充满了空气。
英文内容: ancient castle courtyard style . A large, stone - paved courtyard within the walls of an old castle. The stones are weather - worn and show signs of age. There are small, well - tended gardens with colorful flowers and shrubs. A central fountain may be spraying water, and the sound of birdsong fills the air

内容: 山林小径风格。一条狭窄曲折的小径穿过山坡上的茂密森林。各种树木高耸，枝叶交错。阳光透过树叶，斑驳地照在森林地面上。可以听到附近小溪的流水声，可能还有小森林动物在四处奔跑。
英文内容: mountain forest trail style . A narrow, winding path through a dense forest on the slopes of a mountain. Trees of various species tower overhead, their branches interlaced. Sunlight filters through the foliage, creating dappled light on the forest floor. The sound of a nearby stream can be heard, and there may be small woodland animals scurrying about

内容: 和平的湖畔码头风格。一条木制码头伸入平静、静止的湖中。船只系在码头上，轻轻地在水中摇摆。湖面反射出周围的树木和山脉，形成镜面般的表面。可以听到水拍打码头的声音，附近可能有几只鸭子在游泳。
英文内容: peaceful lakeside dock style . A wooden dock stretching out into a calm, still lake. Boats are tied to the dock, gently bobbing in the water. The lake reflects the surrounding trees and mountains, creating a mirror - like surface. The sound of water lapping against the dock can be heard, and there may be a few ducks swimming nearby

内容: 沙漠绿洲营地风格。在广阔沙漠中心的绿洲附近搭建的一小群帐篷。棕榈树环绕着清澈的蓝色水池。附近拴着骆驼，铺着毯子供人放松。沙丘连绵不断，直到视线尽头，太阳在一片橙色和红色的火光中落下。
英文内容: desert oasis camp style . A small cluster of tents set up near an oasis in the middle of a vast desert. Palm trees surround the clear, blue pool of water. Camels are tied nearby, and there are rugs laid out for relaxation. The sand dunes stretch as far as the eye can see, with the sun setting in a blaze of orange and red

内容: 充满活力的学校操场风格。一个开阔的大操场，绿草如茵。孩子们在秋千、滑梯和攀爬架上玩耍。有篮球场和足球场供学生们进行体育活动。空气中充满了欢声笑语，四周环绕着彩旗或横幅
英文内容: energetic school playground style . A large, open playground with green grass. Children are playing on swings, slides, and climbing frames. There are basketball courts and football fields where students engage in sports. The sound of laughter and shouts fills the air, and there are colorful flags or banners around the perimeter

内容: 热闹的集市广场风格。一个大型、开阔的广场，里面摆满了各种摊位，出售各种各样的商品。五彩缤纷的纺织品、手工艺品和新鲜的农产品陈列着。空气中充满了商贩和顾客讨价还价的嘈杂声。街头艺人表演娱乐人群，广场周围有一些小咖啡馆，人们可以坐在那里享受周围的氛围。
英文内容: lively bazaar square style . A large, open square filled with stalls selling a wide variety of goods. Colorful textiles, handicrafts, and fresh produce are on display. The air is filled with the chatter of vendors and customers bargaining. Street performers entertain the crowd, and there are small cafes around the square where people can sit and enjoy the atmosphere

内容: 儿童房风格。色彩鲜艳、活力四射的墙壁上绘制着卡通人物或幻想场景的壁画。上下铺或主题床，如汽车形状的床。玩具和书籍散落在多彩的储物箱中。可能有一个带有软垫和小桌子供绘画或游戏的玩耍区域。
英文内容: kid's room style . Colorful, vibrant walls with murals of cartoon characters or fantasy scenes. Bunk beds or themed beds, like a car - shaped bed. Toys and books are scattered around in colorful storage bins. There may be a play area with soft mats and a small table for drawing or playing games

内容: 荒野露营风格。一个位于偏远自然区域的露营地，四周被高大的树木和山脉环绕。帐篷搭建在平坦的草地上，篝火熊熊燃烧。可以听到蟋蟀的叫声和火花的噼啪声。夜空中繁星点点，附近可能有一条小溪供取水
英文内容: wilderness campsite style . A campsite in a remote, natural area surrounded by tall trees and mountains. Tents are set up on a flat, grassy area, and there is a campfire burning. The sound of crickets chirping and the crackling of the fire can be heard. The night sky is filled with stars, and there may be a small stream nearby for water

内容: 浪漫樱花公园风格。公园内樱花树盛开，粉色花瓣如地毯般覆盖地面。小路蜿蜒穿过树林，情侣们坐在长椅上欣赏风景。小池塘里养着锦鲤，增添了宁静的氛围，还能听到微风吹动花瓣的轻柔声音
英文内容: romantic cherry blossom park style . A park filled with cherry blossom trees in full bloom, their pink petals covering the ground like a carpet. Paths wind through the trees, and there are benches where couples sit and enjoy the scenery. Small ponds with koi fish add to the peaceful atmosphere, and the soft sound of wind rustling the petals can be heard

内容: 工业风格餐厅风格。裸露的砖墙，金属管道作为天花板灯具，以及带有金属腿的木制餐桌。吊灯中的爱迪生式灯泡创造出温暖的环境光。整体外观粗犷实用，带有一丝城市魅力。
英文内容: industrial - style dining room style . Exposed brick walls, metal pipes for ceiling fixtures, and wooden tables with metal legs. Edison - style bulbs in pendant lights create a warm, ambient glow. The overall look is raw and utilitarian, with a touch of urban charm

内容: 乡村卧室风格。家具采用磨损处理的木材，给人一种舒适、有人居住的感觉。采用大地色调的拼布床品，以及花卉图案的窗帘。可能会有一个真火或假火壁炉来增加温暖。墙壁通常涂成柔和的自然色彩，如米色或浅蓝色。
英文内容: rustic bedroom style . Wooden furniture with a distressed finish, giving a cozy, lived - in feel. Quilted bedding in earthy tones, and floral - printed curtains. There may be a fireplace or a faux - fireplace for added warmth. The walls are often painted in soft, natural colors like beige or light blue

内容: 彗星以行星风格擦过。一颗明亮、冰冷的彗星在太空中急速飞行，其长长的发光尾巴在后面拖着。当它靠近一颗行星时，行星的引力略微影响了彗星的轨迹。由尘埃和气体组成的彗星尾巴，在与行星磁场相互作用时，甚至更加扩散。行星的大气可能会受到彗星经过的影响，在高层大气中引发类似极光的展示。彗星的核是一个黑暗的不规则形状物体，被一层发光的气体和尘埃彗发包围着。
英文内容: comet skimming planet style . A bright, icy comet hurtles through space, its long, glowing tail streaming behind it. As it passes close to a planet, the planet's gravity affects the comet's trajectory slightly. The comet's tail, made of dust and gas, spreads out even more as it interacts with the planet's magnetic field. The planet's atmosphere may be affected by the comet's passing, causing aurora - like displays in the upper atmosphere. The comet's nucleus is a dark, irregular - shaped object, surrounded by a glowing coma of gas and dust
Orchard

内容: 闪耀的银河超新星爆发风格。一片广阔的太空充满了密集的星星群，它们的光芒创造出一幅美丽的多彩挂毯。在中心，一颗巨大的恒星经历了一次超新星爆炸，释放出强烈的能量和光线，照亮了整个银河系。爆炸产生的冲击波在周围的太空中荡漾，使得气体和尘埃云在一系列鲜艳的颜色中发光。银河系中的星星似乎随着这一强大事件的响应而跳舞和闪烁。
英文内容: glittering galaxy supernova eruption style . A vast expanse of space filled with a dense cluster of stars, their light creating a beautiful, multi - colored tapestry. In the center, a massive star undergoes a supernova explosion, releasing an intense burst of energy and light that outshines the entire galaxy. The shockwave from the explosion ripples through the surrounding space, causing the gas and dust clouds to glow in a range of vibrant colors. The stars in the galaxy seem to dance and twinkle in response to the powerful event

内容: 冰川风格。广袤无垠，白色的冰川形态和深蓝色的裂缝。冰是冰冷且坚硬的，可能缓慢移动。周围的区域通常是荒芜的，远处有被雪覆盖的山脉。可能会有融水溪流从冰川流出。
英文内容: glacier style . Vast, white ice formations with deep blue crevasses. The ice is cold and hard, and it may be slowly moving. Surrounding areas are often barren, with snow - covered mountains in the distance. There may be meltwater streams flowing from the glacier
Rainforest
Field

内容: 沙漠风格。广袤无垠的沙丘随风移动。这片土地干旱，植被稀少。阳光强烈，颜色通常是米色、棕色和金色的各种色调。偶尔可能有仙人掌或适应沙漠环境的动物，如骆驼
英文内容: desert style . Vast stretches of sand dunes that shift in the wind. The landscape is arid, with little vegetation. The sun is intense, and the colors are often shades of beige, brown, and gold. There may be occasional cacti or desert - adapted animals like camels

内容: 空间站与卫星群风格。一个大型的多模块空间站漂浮在太空中，其太阳能电池板在阳光下闪闪发光。空间站被一群功能各异的卫星环绕。一些卫星用于通信，其他的用于科学研究或地球观测。这些卫星以协调的方式围绕空间站运行，空间站上的机械臂移动并对其进行服务。空间站的窗户提供了一个广阔太空的视角，远处星星闪烁。
英文内容: space station and satellite swarm style . A large, multi - module space station floating in space, its solar panels glinting in the sunlight. The space station is surrounded by a swarm of satellites, each with its own specific function. Some satellites are used for communication, others for scientific research or Earth observation. The satellites orbit the space station in a coordinated manner, with robotic arms on the space station moving and servicing them. The space station's windows offer a view of the vastness of space, with stars twinkling in the distance

内容: 湿地风格。低洼地区充满水，通常有芦苇、香蒲和其他喜水植物。水很浅，有些地方可能停滞不前。有许多鸟类，如苍鹭和鸭子，以及两栖动物，如青蛙。地面柔软泥泞
英文内容: wetland style . Low - lying areas filled with water, often with reeds, cattails, and other water - loving plants. The water is shallow and may be stagnant in some parts. There are many birds, such as herons and ducks, and amphibians like frogs. The ground is soft and muddy

内容: 河流风格。一条流动的水体，有着水流，蜿蜒穿过景观。河岸可能铺满了岩石、沙子或植被。一些区域可能有小急流，河流上方可能有桥梁横跨。水中游着鱼，河岸附近可以看到鸟儿。
英文内容: river style . A flowing body of water with a current, meandering through the landscape. Riverbanks may be lined with rocks, sand, or vegetation. There could be small rapids in some areas, and bridges spanning the river. Fish swim in the water, and birds may be seen near the banks

内容: 太空碎片和小行星带风格。一个充满混乱太空垃圾的太空区域，包括破损的卫星、被丢弃的火箭部件和旧航天器的碎片。在这些垃圾中，有一个大型的小行星带。小行星的大小不一，从小石块到巨大的月球大小的物体都有。一些小行星有自己的小卫星绕它们运行。太空垃圾和小行星以复杂的模式移动，偶尔相互碰撞，产生明亮的闪光并释放出一阵阵较小的碎片。
英文内容: space debris and asteroid belt style . A region of space filled with a chaotic collection of space debris, including broken satellites, discarded rocket parts, and fragments of old spacecraft. Among the debris, there is a large asteroid belt. The asteroids vary in size, from small boulders to massive, moon - sized objects. Some asteroids have their own small moons orbiting them. The space debris and asteroids move in a complex pattern, occasionally colliding with each other, creating bright flashes of light and releasing a shower of smaller fragments
Aurora / Polar Light

内容: 宇宙尘埃云幻想风景风格。一个巨大的、错综复杂的宇宙尘埃云漂浮在太空中。尘埃粒子被附近恒星的光线照亮，创造出美丽、不断变化的图案。云似乎形成了类似于动物、城堡和其他幻想物体的形状。尘埃云的颜色从柔和的粉红色和紫色到深蓝色，这取决于尘埃的成分和击中它的光线的波长。云非常巨大，以至于可以跨越数光年。
英文内容: cosmic dust cloud fantasy landscape style . A large, intricate cloud of cosmic dust floating in space. The dust particles are illuminated by the light of nearby stars, creating a beautiful, ever - changing pattern. The cloud seems to form shapes reminiscent of animals, castles, and other fantastical objects. The colors of the dust cloud range from soft pinks and purples to deep blues, depending on the composition of the dust and the wavelength of the light hitting it. The cloud is so large that it can span several light - years

内容: 双星系统的引力舞蹈风格。两颗巨大的恒星，一颗是明亮的蓝色巨星，另一颗是红色超巨星，它们以复杂的舞蹈相互绕行。它们的引力作用使它们轻微地扭曲了对方的形状。恒星表面布满了巨大的太阳耀斑和日饵，它们之间的空间充满了带电粒子的流，形成了一座发光的等离子体桥。恒星的光芒照亮了周围的太空，投射出温暖而多彩的光辉。
英文内容: binary star system gravitational dance style . Two massive stars, one a bright blue giant and the other a red supergiant, orbit each other in a complex dance. Their gravitational pull causes them to distort each other's shapes slightly. The stars' surfaces are covered in massive solar flares and prominences, and the space between them is filled with a stream of charged particles, creating a glowing bridge of plasma. The stars' light illuminates the surrounding space, casting a warm and colorful glow

内容: 系外行星独特的地形风格。一个表面与地球任何地方都不同的系外行星。这个星球拥有高耸的水晶状山峰，它们伸向天空，表面反射着星球恒星的光芒，呈现出彩虹般的色彩。广阔的液态甲烷海洋覆盖了星球的大部分地区，海浪拍打着海岸。这个星球的大气层厚重且充满了奇怪的气体，使得天空呈现出独特的颜色，例如深邃的彩虹绿色。这个星球上可能还有活跃的火山，喷发着与地球上不同的熔岩类型。
英文内容: exoplanet's unique terrain style . An exoplanet with a surface unlike any on Earth. The planet has towering, crystal - like mountains that reach towards the sky, their surfaces reflecting the light of the planet's star in a rainbow of colors. There are vast, liquid - methane oceans covering large parts of the planet, with waves crashing against the shorelines. The planet's atmosphere is thick and filled with strange gases, which give the sky a unique color, such as a deep, iridescent green. There may also be active volcanoes on the planet, erupting with a different type of lava than on Earth

内容: 气态巨行星风暴漩涡风格。一个巨大的气态巨行星，其上有着彩色云带环绕。在行星的一个半球上，一个巨大的风暴漩涡肆虐，其规模比地球还要大得多。这个风暴是一个深邃、旋转的云团，其中闪烁着闪电。行星的大气充满了各种气体，这些气体赋予了云朵它们独特的颜色，从深蓝色到鲜艳的橙色。行星的环带由冰和岩石颗粒组成，它们优雅地围绕着行星旋转，反射着行星的光芒。
英文内容: gas giant planet storm vortex style . A colossal gas giant planet, with bands of colorful clouds swirling around it. In one of the planet's hemispheres, a massive storm vortex rages, its size dwarfing that of Earth. The storm is a deep, swirling mass of clouds, with lightning bolts flashing within it. The planet's atmosphere is filled with various gases, which give the clouds their distinct colors, from deep blues to vivid oranges. The planet's rings, made of ice and rock particles, orbit gracefully around it, reflecting the planet's light

内容: 神秘的黑洞吸积盘风格。一个漆黑的空间空洞，周围是一个明亮、旋转的吸积盘。吸积盘由被拉向黑洞事件视界的超热气体和尘埃组成。盘中的气体和尘埃发出从X射线到可见光的强烈辐射，创造出壮观的景象。黑洞的引力非常强大，以至于它扭曲了周围的时空结构，导致附近的恒星沿着奇怪的椭圆形轨道运行。
英文内容: mysterious black hole accretion disk style . A pitch - black void in space, surrounded by a bright, swirling accretion disk. The accretion disk is composed of super - heated gas and dust that is being pulled towards the black hole's event horizon. The gas and dust in the disk emit intense radiation, ranging from X - rays to visible light, creating a spectacular display. The black hole's gravitational pull is so strong that it warps the fabric of space - time around it, causing nearby stars to orbit in strange, elliptical paths

内容: 育婴星团风格。一个巨大的，充满星云的空间区域，新恒星正在诞生。星云是一个庞大的气体和尘埃云，由于附近年轻恒星的辐射而发出柔和的淡彩色光芒。在星云内部，有一些密集的气体团块在自身引力作用下坍缩，形成原恒星。这些原恒星被物质盘包围，最终可能形成行星。这个区域充满了新生和宇宙能量的感觉。
英文内容: nursery star cluster style . A large, nebula - filled region of space where new stars are being born. The nebula is a vast cloud of gas and dust, glowing in soft, pastel colors due to the radiation from nearby young stars. Within the nebula, there are dense pockets of gas that are collapsing under their own gravity, forming protostars. These protostars are surrounded by disks of material, from which planets may eventually form. The area is filled with a sense of new beginnings and cosmic energy
Mountain Range
Cave
Canyon / Gorge

内容: 海洋风格。广阔的蓝绿色水域延伸至地平线, 大浪不断拍打着岸边。空气中弥漫着咸味, 海鸥在头顶盘旋。远处可能有船只或鲸鱼跃出水面。在水下, 可以想象到五彩缤纷的珊瑚礁和成群的鱼
英文内容: ocean style . Expansive blue - green waters stretching to the horizon, with large, rolling waves crashing on the shore. The salty smell fills the air, and seagulls circle above. There may be distant ships or whales breaching the surface. Underwater, colorful coral reefs and schools of fish can be imagined

matte texture style {prompt}. A non - shiny, flat - looking surface that diffuses light rather than reflecting it directly. Gives a more understated, sophisticated look, with a smooth or slightly textured feel
soft texture style {prompt}. The material feels gentle and yielding to the touch, with a flexible and plush quality. It often gives a sense of comfort, such as a soft blanket or a cushion
play-doh style {prompt} . sculpture, clay art, centered composition, Claymation

paint texture style {prompt}. A smooth or slightly textured surface depending on the type of paint. Can have a wide range of colors, with a finish that can be glossy, matte, or semi - gloss, and may show signs of brushstrokes or spray patterns

pearl luster texture style {prompt}. A soft, iridescent sheen similar to that of a pearl, with a smooth surface. The color often has a creamy base with hints of pink, blue, or green in the reflection, giving a luxurious look
amber texture style {prompt}. Fossilized resin surface with golden-orange hue, transparent to translucent quality, and possible inclusion of ancient organisms—like amber gemstones or fossils.

clay texture style {prompt}. Earthy, slightly rough texture with a malleable look as if it has been shaped by hand. Natural color variations ranging from beige to brown, and visible marks from the molding process

rough texture style {prompt}. The surface has a grainy, uneven feel, with visible bumps, ridges, or imperfections. It can add a sense of authenticity and character, like a brick wall or a piece of unfinished wood
texture {prompt} top down close-up
ice texture style {prompt}. Clear to frosty transparent surface with sharp edges, light refraction patterns, and a cold, wet quality—like glacial ice chunks or sculpted ice cubes.

smooth texture style {prompt}. The surface appears sleek, without any roughness or bumps. It reflects light evenly, giving a clean and refined look, such as a polished marble floor or a shiny metal surface
smoke texture style {prompt}. Wispy airborne particle surface with gray/white color, billowing movement, and semi-transparent quality—like cigarette smoke or fog.
hard texture style {prompt}. The surface is firm, resistant to pressure, and has a solid, unyielding feel. It can convey strength and durability, like a block of granite or a metal tool

内容: 宁静的书院，白墙黑瓦的建筑群错落有致。讲堂宽敞明亮，摆放着整齐的桌椅，供学子们听讲学习。藏书楼内，古籍满架，书香四溢。庭院中，有假山、池塘、花草树木，营造出清幽的学习氛围。回廊曲折，连接着各个建筑，学子们在其间漫步、交流。书院大门庄重古朴，彰显着文化的底蕴
英文内容: In the quiet academy, the building complex with white walls and black tiles is arranged in a scattered pattern. The lecture hall is spacious and bright, with neat desks and chairs for students to listen and study. In the library building, ancient books fill the shelves, and the fragrance of books overflows. In the courtyard, there are rockeries, ponds, flowers, plants, and trees, creating a quiet learning atmosphere. The winding corridors connect each building, and students stroll and communicate among them. The main gate of the academy is solemn and simple, showing the cultural heritage

内容: 岭南园林中，庭园建筑群独具特色。建筑多采用青砖、绿瓦，色彩淡雅。镬耳墙高高耸立，具有防火、通风等功能。庭院内，水池清澈，种满荷花。亭台楼阁造型轻盈，装饰着彩色玻璃、灰塑等。墙边的翠竹摇曳生姿，与建筑相映成趣。园中的小径用鹅卵石铺就，图案精美，漫步其中，能感受到浓郁的岭南风情
英文内容: In the Lingnan gardens, the courtyard building complex has its own characteristics. Most of the buildings use blue bricks and green tiles, with elegant colors. The wok-ear walls stand tall, with functions such as fire prevention and ventilation. In the courtyard, the pool is clear and full of lotus flowers. The pavilions, terraces, and towers are of a light and graceful shape, decorated with colored glass, stucco, etc. The bamboo by the wall sways gracefully, forming a beautiful contrast with the buildings. The paths in the garden are paved with cobblestones, with exquisite patterns. Strolling among them, one can feel the strong Lingnan style

内容: 精致的园林中，楼阁建筑群与山水相依。楼阁造型各异，有八角攒尖顶、四角方亭等。楼阁的门窗雕花精美，朱红的立柱与青灰的瓦檐相互映衬。楼阁内，陈设着古朴的家具和书画。园林内，假山堆叠，池塘中荷花盛开。楼阁的倒影在水中摇曳，与周围的花草树木构成一幅美丽的画卷。微风拂过，楼阁檐下的风铃轻响，增添了几分灵动的气息
英文内容: In the exquisite garden, the pavilion building complex is adjacent to the mountains and waters. The pavilions are of various shapes, such as octagonal spire roofs and four-cornered square pavilions. The doors and windows of the pavilions are exquisitely carved, and the vermilion pillars contrast with the gray tile eaves. Inside the pavilions, simple and ancient furniture and calligraphy and paintings are displayed. In the garden, the rockeries are stacked, and the lotus flowers are in full bloom in the pond. The reflections of the pavilions sway in the water, forming a beautiful picture with the surrounding flowers, plants, and trees. When the breeze blows, the wind chimes under the eaves of the pavilions tinkle, adding a bit of agility

内容: 苏州园林中，宅园相依的建筑群别具韵味。粉墙环绕，月洞门、漏窗点缀其间。宅院内，厅堂轩敞，木雕、砖雕、石雕工艺精湛。家具陈设古朴典雅，书画墨宝悬挂于壁。园林内，假山堆叠、池塘清幽，亭台楼阁错落有致。曲折的回廊连接着各个建筑，漫步其中，步移景异，尽显江南园林的精致与婉约
英文内容: In the Suzhou gardens, the building complex where the residence and the garden are adjacent has a unique charm. The whitewashed walls surround it, and moon gates and lattice windows are dotted among them. In the residence, the halls are spacious, and the wood carvings, brick carvings, and stone carvings are of exquisite craftsmanship. The furniture and furnishings are simple and elegant, and calligraphy and paintings are hung on the walls. In the garden, the rockeries are stacked, the ponds are quiet, and the pavilions, terraces, and towers are arranged in a scattered pattern. The winding corridors connect each building. Strolling among them, the scenery changes at every step, showing the delicacy and grace of the Jiangnan gardens

内容: 京城的四合院，青灰色的院墙围合出一方宁静天地。朱红色的大门庄重典雅，门墩雕刻精美。进入大门，影壁上的吉祥图案寓意美好。四合院中，正房高大宽敞，长辈居住于此。东西厢房相对而立，晚辈居住其中。庭院内，种着海棠、石榴等树木，夏季绿树成荫，秋季果实累累。中间的方砖铺地，摆放着石桌石凳，家人在此聊天、休憩，充满生活气息
英文内容: In the quadrangles in the capital city, the grayish-blue courtyard walls enclose a peaceful world. The vermilion gate is solemn and elegant, and the door piers are exquisitely carved. Entering the gate, the auspicious patterns on the screen wall imply good fortune. In the quadrangle, the main house is tall and spacious, where the elders live. The east and west wing rooms stand opposite each other, where the younger generations live. In the courtyard, trees such as crabapple and pomegranate are planted. In summer, the trees provide shade, and in autumn, the fruits are abundant. The square bricks in the middle are paved on the ground, and stone tables and stools are placed. Family members chat and rest here, full of the flavor of life

内容: 深山之中，寺庙古刹建筑群庄严神圣。红墙金瓦的大雄宝殿气势磅礴，殿内佛像高大威严，香烟袅袅。钟鼓楼分立两侧，晨钟暮鼓，声传悠远。藏经楼古朴厚重，收藏着众多佛教经典。寺庙内的庭院中，古木参天，石碑林立。石凳上，僧人或坐或立，诵经修行。周围的山林郁郁葱葱，为寺庙增添了几分清幽与宁静
英文内容: In the deep mountains, the temple complex is solemn and sacred. The Mahavira Hall with red walls and golden tiles is magnificent. The Buddha statues in the hall are tall and majestic, with curling incense. The bell tower and the drum tower stand on both sides. The morning bell and the evening drum sound far and wide. The scripture storage building is simple and thick, collecting numerous Buddhist scriptures. In the courtyard of the temple, ancient trees reach into the sky, and stone tablets stand in great numbers. On the stone benches, monks sit or stand, chanting scriptures and practicing. The surrounding mountains and forests are lush and green, adding a bit of tranquility and peace to the temple

内容: 群山环绕的客家土楼，巨大的圆形或方形土楼错落分布。土楼外墙厚实，由生土、砂石等材料夯筑而成，具有坚固的防御功能。土楼内部，环形或方形的房屋围绕着中间的天井而建，形成一个大家庭聚居的空间。天井采光通风，是人们活动的中心。土楼内的木雕、石雕等装饰精美，体现了客家文化的独特魅力。楼外，农田翠绿，小溪潺潺，展现出田园风光的宁静与美好
英文内容: In the Hakka tulou surrounded by mountains, the huge circular or square tulou are scattered in a disorderly manner. The outer walls of the tulou are thick, rammed with materials such as raw earth and sand and gravel, with a strong defensive function. Inside the tulou, the circular or square houses are built around the central patio, forming a living space for a large family. The patio provides lighting and ventilation and is the center of people's activities. The wood carvings, stone carvings, and other decorations in the tulou are exquisite, reflecting the unique charm of Hakka culture. Outside the building, the farmland is green, and the small stream gurgles, showing the tranquility and beauty of the rural scenery

内容: 热闹的古镇集市，由各种店铺、摊位组成的建筑群熙熙攘攘。青石板街道两旁，木质的店铺门面各具特色，有卖小吃的、卖手工艺品的、卖生活用品的。店铺的招牌五颜六色，吸引着顾客的目光。集市中央，有一座古老的戏台，偶尔会有戏曲表演。周围的人群围聚观看，喝彩声不断。集市的建筑风格充满了生活气息，展现出古镇的繁华与活力
英文内容: In the bustling ancient town market, the building complex composed of various shops and stalls is bustling. On both sides of the bluestone street, the wooden shop fronts have their own characteristics, selling snacks, handicrafts, daily necessities, etc. The signboards of the shops are colorful, attracting the attention of customers. In the center of the market, there is an ancient stage, and occasionally there are opera performances. The surrounding crowd gathers to watch, with continuous applause. The architectural style of the market is full of the flavor of life, showing the prosperity and vitality of the ancient town

内容: 繁华的码头古镇，沿河岸而建的商埠建筑群热闹非凡。木质的楼阁、店铺鳞次栉比，招牌幌子随风飘动。楼阁内，商人们洽谈生意，货物堆积如山。街道上，石板路被行人踩踏得光滑，挑夫们肩挑货物匆匆而过。河边，停靠的商船桅杆林立，装卸货物的号子声此起彼伏。古镇的建筑风格融合了多种元素，展现出独特的商业文化魅力
英文内容: In the bustling dock ancient town, the commercial port building complex built along the riverbank is extremely lively. The wooden pavilions and shops are row upon row, and the signboards and banners flutter in the wind. Inside the pavilions, merchants negotiate business, and the goods pile up like mountains. On the street, the stone road is worn smooth by pedestrians, and porters rush by with goods on their shoulders. By the river, the masts of the moored merchant ships stand in great numbers, and the chanting sounds of loading and unloading goods rise and fall one after another. The architectural style of the ancient town integrates various elements, showing the unique charm of commercial culture

内容: 青山环抱的徽派古村落，灰白色马头墙层层叠叠，在蓝天映衬下格外醒目。高墙深院的民居错落有致，庭院内有精美的木雕、石雕、砖雕装饰。天井采光，雨水落入 “四水归堂” 的水池。村前的小溪潺潺流淌，溪边妇女们在洗衣洗菜。村口的古牌坊庄重肃穆，雕刻着历史故事，彰显着家族荣耀
英文内容: In the Huizhou-style ancient village surrounded by green mountains, the gray-white horse-head walls are stacked layer upon layer, particularly eye-catching against the blue sky. The residential houses with high walls and deep courtyards are arranged in a scattered and orderly manner. The courtyards are decorated with exquisite wood carvings, stone carvings, and brick carvings. The patio provides lighting, and rainwater falls into the pool of "four waters returning to the hall." The small stream in front of the village gurgles, and women are washing clothes and vegetables by the stream. The ancient memorial archway at the entrance of the village is solemn and solemn, carved with historical stories, showing the family's glory

内容: 水乡之中，廊桥建筑群横跨河道。廊桥的桥身用青石砌成，桥上建木质廊屋。廊屋的廊柱为浅棕色，廊顶覆青瓦。廊屋两侧设有长椅，供行人休息。廊桥的门窗雕花精美，具有浓郁的水乡特色。桥下，河水清澈，鱼儿嬉戏。桥边，垂柳依依，随风飘舞。行人在廊桥上漫步，可欣赏水乡的美景，感受水乡的温婉与宁静
英文内容: In the water town, the covered bridge complex spans the river. The bridge body of the covered bridge is made of bluestone, and a wooden corridor is built on the bridge. The corridor pillars of the corridor are light brown, and the corridor roof is covered with green tiles. Benches are set on both sides of the corridor for pedestrians to rest. The doors and windows of the covered bridge are exquisitely carved, with a strong water town characteristic. Under the bridge, the river water is clear, and fish are playing. By the bridge, the weeping willows are swaying in the wind. Pedestrians stroll on the covered bridge, enjoying the beautiful scenery of the water town and feeling the gentleness and tranquility of the water town

内容: 云雾缭绕的仙山之上，道观建筑群若隐若现。道观的殿宇飞檐斗拱，气势恢宏。青瓦白墙，与周围的青山绿水融为一体。殿内供奉着道教神仙，香烟缭绕。观内的庭院中，种着苍松翠柏，宁静清幽。道士们身着道袍，在庭院中修炼、诵经。山脚下，潺潺的溪流声伴随着道观的钟声，营造出超凡脱俗的仙境氛围
英文内容: On the fairy mountain shrouded in clouds and mist, the Taoist temple complex looms. The halls of the Taoist temple have overhanging eaves and dougong, with an imposing manner. The green tiles and white walls blend in with the surrounding green mountains and clear waters. Inside the hall, Taoist immortals are enshrined, with curling incense. In the courtyard of the temple, there are green pines and cypresses, quiet and peaceful. The Taoist priests, dressed in Taoist robes, practice and chant scriptures in the courtyard. At the foot of the mountain, the gurgling sound of the stream accompanies the bell sound of the Taoist temple, creating an otherworldly fairyland atmosphere

内容: 皇家园林内，宏伟的宫殿建筑群气势恢宏。红墙黄瓦在阳光照耀下熠熠生辉，汉白玉台阶和栏杆雕刻精美。宫殿飞檐斗拱，装饰着金龙和玺彩画。宫殿前的广场宽阔平整，可举行盛大仪式。宫殿周边，古松翠柏环绕，与宫殿相映成趣。远处的湖光山色，为宫殿建筑群增添了几分灵动与秀丽
英文内容: In the imperial garden, the magnificent palace complex is imposing. The red walls and yellow tiles shine brightly in the sun. The white marble steps and railings are exquisitely carved. The palaces have overhanging eaves and dougong, decorated with dragon and xi paintings. The square in front of the palace is wide and flat, where grand ceremonies can be held. Around the palaces, ancient pine and cypress trees surround them, forming a beautiful contrast with the palaces. The lake and mountain scenery in the distance adds a bit of agility and beauty to the palace complex

内容: 江南水乡，河道蜿蜒穿镇而过，两岸是粉墙黛瓦的民居建筑群。木质门窗雕花精美，飞檐翘角错落有致。临河的楼阁设有美人靠，居民在窗边晾衣、闲聊。河上乌篷船悠悠划过，船头挂着红灯笼，船桨拨开水面，泛起层层涟漪。远处，一座石拱桥横跨河道，连接着两岸街巷，构成一幅宁静祥和的水乡画卷
英文内容: In the Jiangnan water town, the river winds through the town. On both banks are residential building complexes with whitewashed walls and black tiles. The wooden doors and windows are exquisitely carved, and the overhanging eaves and upturned corners are arranged in a scattered pattern. There are beauty rails in the riverside pavilions. Residents hang out their clothes and chat by the windows. A wupeng boat paddles slowly on the river, with red lanterns hanging at the bow. The oars break through the water, creating layers of ripples. In the distance, a stone arch bridge spans the river, connecting the streets on both banks, forming a peaceful and harmonious water town picture

内容: 青山绿水间，山间别墅建筑群错落分布。别墅多采用木质结构，与自然环境相得益彰。别墅的庭院中，繁花似锦，绿草如茵。亭台楼阁点缀其间，供主人休闲娱乐。从别墅的窗户望去，远处的山峦连绵起伏，云雾缭绕。山间的小溪在别墅旁潺潺流过，清澈见底。漫步在山间小径，花香鸟语，让人仿佛置身于世外桃源
英文内容: Among the green mountains and clear waters, the mountain villa complex is scattered. Most of the villas adopt a wooden structure, complementing the natural environment. In the courtyard of the villa, the flowers are in full bloom, and the grass is like a green carpet. Pavilions, terraces, and towers are dotted among them for the owner to relax and entertain. Looking out from the windows of the villa, the distant mountains stretch in a continuous line, shrouded in clouds and mist. The small stream in the mountains gurgles beside the villa, clear to the bottom. Strolling on the mountain path, with the fragrance of flowers and the chirping of birds, one seems to be in a paradise

内容: 气派的庄园府邸，高墙深院的建筑群庄重典雅。府邸的大门高大宽阔，门楣上雕刻着精美的图案。进入大门，是宽敞的庭院，地面用青砖铺就。正房宏伟壮观，采用抬梁式木构架，装饰着精美的木雕、石雕。东西厢房对称分布，供家人居住或用作书房、客房等。庭院中，种着名贵的花卉和树木，设有假山、池塘。庄园内的建筑布局严谨，体现了主人的身份和地位
英文内容: The magnificent manor mansion, the building complex with high walls and deep courtyards is solemn and elegant. The main gate of the mansion is tall and wide, and the lintel is carved with exquisite patterns. Entering the gate, there is a spacious courtyard, and the ground is paved with blue bricks. The main house is magnificent, adopting a beam-lifting wooden frame and decorated with exquisite wood carvings and stone carvings. The east and west wing rooms are symmetrically distributed, for family members to live in or used as study rooms, guest rooms, etc. In the courtyard, precious flowers and trees are planted, and there are rockeries and ponds. The architectural layout in the manor is rigorous, reflecting the owner's status and position

内容: 体型如房屋大小，黑色甲壳，多条带绒毛的长腿，能吐坚韧蛛丝缠绕猎物，产卵孵化小蜘蛛
英文内容: House-sized build, black carapace, multiple fluffy long legs, can spin tough spider silk to entangle prey, lays eggs to hatch small spiders

内容: 蓝色皮肤，耐寒怕火，肢体断裂后可快速再生
英文内容: Blue skin, cold-resistant but afraid of fire, limbs can regenerate quickly after breaking

内容: 黑色毛发，三只狗头，眼睛泛红，能喷火，嗅觉敏锐追踪目标
英文内容: Black fur, three dog heads, red eyes, can breathe fire, sharp sense of smell to track targets

内容: 多条粗壮触手，吸盘带倒刺，能喷墨逃生，牙齿锋利可咬碎甲壳
英文内容: Multiple thick tentacles, suction cups with barbs, can spray ink to escape, sharp teeth can crush carapaces

内容: 多颗蛇头（砍断会再生），蛇身粗壮，毒液致命
英文内容: Multiple snake heads (regrow when cut off), thick snake body, and deadly venom

内容: 体型巨大如蛇，生活在沙漠地下，体表有硬甲，能吞噬车辆和生物
英文内容: Giant snake-like build, lives underground in deserts, has hard armor on the body surface, can swallow vehicles and creatures

内容: 冰蓝色身体，由冰块和寒霜组成，能呼出寒气冻结目标，脚步声可引发冰裂
英文内容: Ice-blue body, composed of ice blocks and frost, can breathe cold air to freeze targets, footsteps can cause ice cracks

内容: 石质外壳，夜间活动，能飞行，利爪可撕裂盔甲
英文内容: Stone shell, active at night, can fly, claws can tear armor

内容: 皮肤苍白，红色瞳孔，能变形为蝙蝠，惧怕阳光和大蒜，可操控低级吸血鬼
英文内容: Pale skin, red pupils, can transform into a bat, afraid of sunlight and garlic, can control low-level vampires

内容: 体型庞大，额头单只巨眼，力大无穷，擅长锻造
英文内容: Giant build, single large eye on the forehead, immense strength, good at forging

内容: 覆盖鳞片、带巨翼，能喷吐火焰 / 冰霜，爪子锋利
英文内容: Covered in scales, with large wings, can breathe fire/ice, and has sharp claws

内容: 女性幽灵形态，长发苍白，哭声能预示死亡，对生者有精神冲击
英文内容: Female ghost form, pale long hair, cry can predict death, has mental impact on the living

内容: 全身覆盖灰棕毛发，体型比普通狼大，獠牙外露，速度快且力量强
英文内容: Covered in gray-brown fur all over, larger than ordinary wolves, fangs exposed, fast and strong

内容: 树干为躯干，树枝为手臂，根系可作为双脚移动，能挥舞枝干抽打敌人，可吸收周围植物能量
英文内容: Trunk as torso, branches as arms, roots can be used as feet to move, can wave branches to whip enemies, can absorb energy from surrounding plants

内容: 鹰头鹰翼 + 狮身狮尾，性情凶猛，擅长俯冲捕猎
英文内容: Eagle head and wings + lion body and tail, ferocious temperament, good at diving to hunt

内容: 由熔岩构成，体表燃烧火焰，体温极高，触碰会灼烧，能投掷熔岩块
英文内容: Composed of lava, flames burning on the body surface, extremely high body temperature, burning on touch, can throw lava blocks

内容: 龟壳坚硬带龙鳞，头部似龙，可在水陆快速移动，擅长撞击
英文内容: Hard turtle shell with dragon scales, dragon-like head, can move quickly on land and water, good at ramming

内容: 狮身人面，尾部长有毒刺，能喷射毒针攻击
英文内容: Lion body with human face, poisonous stinger on the tail, can shoot poisonous needles to attack

内容: 狮头、羊身、蛇尾，能喷火，具备三种生物的攻击能力
英文内容: Lion head, goat body, snake tail, can breathe fire, and has attack abilities of three creatures

内容: 红色皮肤，带蝙蝠翼和弯角，手持恶魔镰刀，能召唤小恶魔，释放地狱火焰
英文内容: Red skin, with bat wings and curved horns, holds a demon scythe, can summon small demons, and release hellfire

内容: （高层现代住宅建筑：1.2），流线型的城市建筑，开阔的玻璃窗户，宽敞的阳台，现代的外观，干净的线条，极简主义设计，融入的绿化，明亮的室内，豪华的生活空间

内容: 外貌与本体完全一致（基因相同），成长速度可快可慢，无自主意识（或后期觉醒），多作为本体的 “替代品” 或 “工具”
英文内容: Identical appearance to the original (same genes); growth rate can be fast or slow; no self-awareness (or awakens later); mostly used as a substitute or tool for the original

内容: 皮肤青灰或苍白，身体僵硬（关节活动受限），行动缓慢，畏惧阳光与糯米，被其咬伤会感染，无自主意识（多受操控）
英文内容: Grayish-blue or pale skin; stiff body (limited joint movement); slow movement; afraid of sunlight and glutinous rice; being bitten by it causes infection; no self-awareness (mostly controlled)

内容: 体型小巧（约 50 厘米），人身带花瓣装饰（多为裙摆或发饰，颜色鲜艳如玫瑰、百合），身体散发花香，擅长操控花瓣与花粉（可制造幻觉），多居住在花丛中，性格活泼且娇俏
英文内容: Small figure (about 50 cm tall); human body decorated with flower petals (mostly as skirts or hair accessories, bright colors like roses and lilies); emits floral fragrance; good at controlling petals and pollen (can create illusions); mostly lives in flower clusters; lively and cute personality

内容: 可模仿任意人形（包括外貌与声音），本体多为模糊的液态或半透明形态，擅长伪装与间谍活动，无固定外形特征
英文内容: Can imitate any human form (including appearance and voice); original form is mostly an ambiguous liquid or semi-transparent form; good at disguise and espionage; no fixed appearance features

内容: 人身带发光器官（如头部、胸部有荧光斑点，适应深海黑暗），皮肤呈深蓝色或黑色（抗高压），鳃部更发达（可在深海呼吸），擅长在高压深海活动，能发出低频声波沟通，性格孤僻且谨慎
英文内容: Human body with luminous organs (such as fluorescent spots on head and chest, adapting to deep-sea darkness); dark blue or black skin (resistant to high pressure); more developed gills (can breathe in deep sea); good at moving in high-pressure deep sea; can emit low-frequency sound waves for communication; lonely and cautious personality

内容: 体型高大（3-5 米），皮肤多为灰色或棕色，再生能力极强（除火焰攻击外伤口易愈合），长相丑陋，性格残暴且智力较低
英文内容: Tall figure (3-5 meters), skin mostly gray or brown; extremely strong regenerative ability (wounds heal easily except from fire attacks); ugly appearance, cruel and low-intelligence

内容: 继承兽人的绿皮肤与人类的体型（比兽人纤细），獠牙较短，擅长近身格斗与生存技能，性格勇猛但比兽人更理智
英文内容: Inherits orc's green skin and human's figure (slenderer than orcs); shorter fangs; good at close combat and survival skills; brave but more rational than orcs

标题: 克隆人（变种：增强型克隆人）
内容: 外貌与本体一致，但身体机能强化（如力量、速度提升 2 倍），体内植入强化芯片（可连接科技设备），有自主意识但忠诚度受程序控制，擅长执行高难度任务，性格冷静且高效
英文内容: Identical appearance to the original, but enhanced physical functions (such as 2x strength and speed); implanted with an enhancement chip (can connect to technological devices); has self-awareness but loyalty controlled by programs; good at performing high-difficulty tasks; calm and efficient personality

内容: 人身由树木构成（皮肤似树皮，带纹理），头发为树叶（颜色随季节变化，春绿秋黄），可与植物沟通，能从大地吸收养分，擅长操控藤蔓，性格沉稳且热爱自然
英文内容: Human body made of wood (bark-like skin with texture); hair is leaves (color changes with seasons: green in spring, yellow in autumn); can communicate with plants; absorbs nutrients from the earth; good at controlling vines; calm and nature-loving personality

内容: 人身带大型膜翼（类似蝙蝠翼，可长途飞行），骨骼轻盈（适应飞行），皮肤呈淡紫色（可抵御宇宙辐射），擅长星际航行与空中战斗，以部落为单位生活，性格骄傲且重视荣誉
英文内容: Human body with large membrane wings (bat-like, for long-distance flight); light bones (adapted to flight); light purple skin (resistant to cosmic radiation); good at interstellar navigation and air combat; lives in tribes; proud and honor-focused personality

内容: 继承精灵的尖耳朵与人类的身材（中等身高），寿命比人类长但比精灵短，擅长弓箭与基础魔法，性格兼具精灵的灵动与人类的务实
英文内容: Inherits elf's pointed ears and human's figure (medium height); lifespan longer than humans but shorter than elves; good at archery and basic magic; personality has both elf's agility and human's practicality

内容: 长轴距低趴车身，大尺寸宽幅后胎，圆形复古大灯，裸露式 V 缸引擎，简约单座设计
英文内容: Long wheelbase and low-slung body, large-sized wide rear tire, round retro headlight, exposed V-cylinder engine, simple single-seat design

内容: 激进街车风格，异形 LED 大灯（三角形），单摇臂，裸露式后摇臂，短尾单座，碳纤维小部件点缀
英文内容: Aggressive street bike style, irregular LED headlight (triangular), single-sided swingarm, exposed rear swingarm, short tail single seat, carbon fiber small parts decoration

内容: 复古街车风格，圆形 LED 大灯（带光环），裸露式车架，短尾设计，经典圆形后视镜，辐条式轮毂
英文内容: Retro street bike style, round LED headlight (with light ring), exposed frame, short tail design, classic round rearview mirrors, spoked wheels

内容: ADV 越野风格，高耸的风挡，双圆形大灯，鸟嘴式车头，辐条式轮毂（适配越野胎），边箱支架预留位
英文内容: ADV off-road style, tall windshield, dual round headlights, beak-shaped front end, spoked wheels (for off-road tires), side box bracket reserved

内容: 流线型仿赛车身，锐利双 LED 大灯（呈鹰嘴状），高耸的尾部定风翼，侧置单出排气，多辐式运动轮毂
英文内容: Streamlined sportbike body, sharp dual LED headlights (in eagle beak shape), tall rear spoiler, side-mounted single exhaust, multi-spoke sport wheels

内容: 鲨鱼鼻式车头，LED 大灯集成日行灯（呈 Y 型），单摇臂设计，大面积碳纤维饰板，尾部紧凑且上扬
英文内容: Shark-nose front end, LED headlights integrated with daytime running lights (in Y shape), single-sided swingarm design, large-area carbon fiber panels, compact and upward-angled rear

内容: 经典巡航风格，大型圆形大灯（带镀铬装饰），长车把，宽大皮质双座，镀铬排气（双边双出），复古轮毂造型
英文内容: Classic cruiser style, large round headlight (with chrome decoration), long handlebars, wide leather dual seats, chrome exhaust (dual exit on both sides), retro wheel design

内容: 复古 bobber 风格，短轴距车身，圆形大灯，单座（皮质），外露式车架，辐条轮毂配白墙胎
英文内容: Retro bobber style, short wheelbase body, round headlight, single seat (leather), exposed frame, spoked wheels with whitewall tires

内容: 街跑风格，锐利 LED 大灯（分体式），裸露式引擎，短尾设计，单出排气（高位），运动化轮毂
英文内容: Street sport style, sharp LED headlights (split type), exposed engine, short tail design, single exhaust (high position), sporty wheels

标题: 希腊蓝白建筑（圣托里尼岛建筑）
内容: 希腊圣托里尼岛，蓝白建筑沿火山悬崖分布，房屋外墙为白色（粉刷光滑），屋顶与门窗框为蓝色（明亮的天蓝色）。建筑多为两层（带露台，露台上摆放蓝色桌椅与三角梅），露台边缘有白色栏杆。傍晚时分，夕阳将天空染成橙红色，蓝白建筑与海面的倒影交织，游客们在露台上欣赏日落，海风拂过，浪漫又惬意
英文内容: On Santorini Island, Greece, the blue-and-white buildings are distributed along the volcanic cliffs; the outer walls of the houses are white (smoothly painted), and the roofs and door/window frames are blue (bright sky blue). Most buildings are two-story (with terraces, where blue tables, chairs and bougainvillea are placed); there are white railings on the terrace edges. In the evening, the sunset dyes the sky orange-red; the blue-and-white buildings interweave with the reflection on the sea; tourists enjoy the sunset on the terraces; the sea breeze blows, romantic and comfortable

内容: 德国巴伐利亚山区，新天鹅堡坐落在山顶，白色墙体搭配深蓝色屋顶（尖顶错落）。城堡外立面有多个尖塔与拱窗（窗棂为黑色铁艺），正面有宽阔的露台（俯瞰山谷）。城堡周围是茂密的森林，山谷中有湖泊（湖水清澈，倒映城堡身影），云雾缭绕时，城堡似漂浮在山间的童话建筑，游客们在山脚下仰望，仿佛走进奇幻世界
英文内容: In the Bavarian mountains of Germany, Neuschwanstein Castle sits on the top of a mountain, with white walls and dark blue roofs (scattered spires). The outer facade of the castle has multiple spires and arched windows (black iron window grilles), and a wide terrace (overlooking the valley) on the front. The castle is surrounded by dense forests, and there is a lake in the valley (clear water reflecting the castle); when mist shrouds, the castle looks like a fairy-tale building floating in the mountains; tourists look up at the foot of the mountain, as if entering a fantasy world

标题: 法式庄园城堡（卢瓦尔河谷城堡）
内容: 法国卢瓦尔河谷，庄园城堡临河而建，主体建筑为灰白色石材（屋顶是蓝色石板瓦）。城堡有多个圆形塔楼（顶端呈圆锥形），塔楼之间有城墙连接（城墙上有垛口）。城堡前是法式花园（对称的几何花坛，种着修剪整齐的黄杨），花园通向河流，河上有石桥连接对岸，清晨时分，薄雾笼罩花园，城堡的影子映在河中，优雅又静谧
英文内容: In the Loire Valley of France, the manor castle is built by the river, with the main building made of gray-white stone (roof covered with blue slate tiles). The castle has multiple circular towers (conical tops), connected by city walls (with crenels on the walls). In front of the castle is a French garden (symmetrical geometric flower beds, planted with neatly trimmed boxwood); the garden leads to the river, with a stone bridge connecting the other bank; in the early morning, mist shrouds the garden, and the castle's shadow is reflected in the river, elegant and quiet

标题: 瑞典斯堪的纳维亚风格木屋（斯德哥尔摩郊区木屋）
内容: 斯德哥尔摩郊区，斯堪的纳维亚风格木屋线条简洁，外墙为浅棕色木材（保留自然纹理），屋顶是深灰色金属瓦（坡度平缓）。门窗为白色（大尺寸玻璃窗，增加采光），屋前有小花园（种着耐寒的三色堇与云杉）。冬季时屋顶覆盖薄雪，屋檐下挂着冰棱，屋内灯光透过玻璃窗透出，与周围的森林相映，简约又温馨
英文内容: In the suburbs of Stockholm, the Scandinavian-style wooden house has simple lines; the outer wall is light brown wood (retaining natural texture); the roof is covered with dark gray metal tiles (gentle slope). The doors and windows are white (large glass windows to increase lighting); there is a small garden in front of the house (planted with cold-resistant pansies and spruces). In winter, the roof is covered with thin snow; icicles hang under the eaves; warm light shines through the glass windows, contrasting with the surrounding forest, simple and warm

标题: 比利时布鲁塞尔大广场建筑（行会大楼）
内容: 布鲁塞尔大广场，四周是 17 世纪行会大楼，建筑风格多样（哥特式、巴洛克式混合）。外立面色彩丰富（红、金、棕等），墙面有壁画与浮雕（描绘行业场景），屋顶有尖塔与雕像（象征行会身份）。广场地面铺青石板，中央有青铜喷泉，周末时广场举办鲜花市场，五颜六色的鲜花与古老建筑相映，热闹又典雅
英文内容: In Brussels Grand Place, surrounded by 17th-century guildhouses, with a mix of architectural styles (Gothic, Baroque). The outer facades are colorful (red, gold, brown, etc.), with murals and reliefs on the walls (depicting industry scenes), and spires and statues on the roofs (symbolizing guild identity). The square is paved with bluestone; there is a bronze fountain in the center; a flower market is held on weekends; colorful flowers contrast with the ancient buildings, lively and elegant

标题: 葡萄牙曼努埃尔式建筑（里斯本热罗尼莫斯修道院）
内容: 里斯本港口旁，热罗尼莫斯修道院是曼努埃尔式风格，外立面用浅色石灰岩砌筑，布满复杂的石雕（航海元素、宗教符号）。修道院正门为拱形（拱顶有多层浮雕），窗户细长（哥特式与文艺复兴式结合）。修道院前是宽阔的广场，广场上有青铜雕像，海鸥在广场上空飞翔，海风带来海水气息，建筑在阳光下显得庄重又宏伟
英文内容: Next to the Lisbon port, Jerónimos Monastery is in Manueline style; the outer facade is built with light-colored limestone, covered with complex stone carvings (nautical elements, religious symbols). The main entrance of the monastery is arched (with multi-layer reliefs on the vault), and the windows are slender (combination of Gothic and Renaissance styles). In front of the monastery is a wide square, with bronze statues on the square; seagulls fly over the square; the sea breeze brings the smell of seawater; the building looks solemn and magnificent in the sun

标题: 西班牙式庭院住宅（安达卢西亚庭院）
内容: 西班牙安达卢西亚地区，庭院住宅中央是方形天井，天井地面铺彩色马赛克瓷砖（图案多为几何或花卉）。四周建筑为两层（白色外墙，蓝色门窗框），二楼有木质阳台（挂着彩色陶罐与绿植）。天井中央设喷泉（石雕喷泉，水流潺潺），墙角种着橙树与九重葛（紫色花朵垂落墙面），傍晚时分，居民在天井里乘凉聊天，灯光照亮瓷砖，温馨又热闹
英文内容: In the Andalusia region of Spain, the courtyard house has a square patio in the center, paved with colorful mosaic tiles (mostly geometric or floral patterns). The surrounding buildings are two-story (white outer walls, blue door and window frames), with wooden balconies on the second floor (hanging colorful pottery pots and green plants). A stone-carved fountain (with gurgling water) is in the center of the patio; orange trees and bougainvillea (purple flowers hanging on the wall) are planted at the corners; in the evening, residents cool off and chat in the patio; lights illuminate the tiles, warm and lively

标题: 英式乡村别墅（科茨沃尔德石屋）
内容: 英国科茨沃尔德地区，乡村别墅由当地米黄色石灰岩砌筑，屋顶覆盖灰色石板瓦（坡度较陡）。烟囱呈圆柱形（多根错落分布），门窗框为黑色（木质，线条简洁）。别墅周围是绿色草坪，草坪上散布着白色野花，花园里种着玫瑰与薰衣草，一条石子路从大门通向主屋，门前挂着木质门牌，雨后石板路泛着光泽，充满田园气息
英文内容: In the Cotswolds region of the UK, the country villa is built with local buff limestone, and the roof is covered with gray slate tiles (steep slope). The chimneys are cylindrical (multiple scattered), and the door and window frames are black (wooden, simple lines). Around the villa is a green lawn, dotted with white wildflowers; roses and lavender are planted in the garden; a stone path leads from the gate to the main house; a wooden house plate hangs in front of the door; the stone path glows after rain, full of rural charm

标题: 哥特式大教堂（巴黎圣母院）
内容: 巴黎街头，哥特式大教堂巍峨矗立，尖塔直插云霄（最高塔达 69 米）。外立面布满精致的石雕（圣经故事浮雕），玫瑰窗直径约 13 米（彩色玻璃拼接出宗教图案），飞扶壁如骨架般支撑着墙体。阳光透过玫瑰窗，在教堂内部投下斑斓光影，信徒们在祭坛前虔诚祈祷，钟声敲响时，声音传遍整个街区，庄严又神圣
英文内容: On the streets of Paris, the Gothic cathedral stands towering, with spires piercing the sky (the tallest tower is 69 meters). The outer facade is covered with exquisite stone carvings (reliefs of Bible stories), the rose window is about 13 meters in diameter (stained glass pieced into religious patterns), and flying buttresses support the walls like skeletons. Sunlight filters through the rose window, casting colorful light and shadow inside the church; believers pray devoutly in front of the altar; when the bell rings, the sound spreads throughout the neighborhood, solemn and sacred

标题: 俄罗斯东正教教堂（莫斯科圣瓦西里大教堂）
内容: 莫斯科红场旁，圣瓦西里大教堂造型独特，由 9 个彩色洋葱头状穹顶组成（颜色分别为红、蓝、绿、金等，穹顶表面有螺旋纹）。教堂墙体为红色（砖结构），门窗框为白色（雕刻精美花纹）。教堂周围是红色砖墙，广场上飘扬着俄罗斯国旗，信徒们在教堂前点燃蜡烛，节日时教堂周围挂满彩灯，绚丽又庄严
英文内容: Next to Red Square in Moscow, St. Basil's Cathedral has a unique shape, composed of 9 colorful onion-shaped domes (colors include red, blue, green, gold, etc., with spiral patterns on the dome surface). The church walls are red (brick structure), and the door and window frames are white (exquisitely carved patterns). The church is surrounded by red brick walls; the Russian flag flutters in the square; believers light candles in front of the church; colorful lights are hung around the church during festivals, gorgeous and solemn

标题: 文艺复兴式别墅（佛罗伦萨美第奇别墅）
内容: 佛罗伦萨郊外，文艺复兴式别墅坐落在山坡上，整体呈对称布局（中央主建筑 + 两侧辅楼）。外墙用浅黄色石材砌筑，门窗为拱形（拱券边缘有浮雕装饰），屋顶是红色陶瓦（坡度平缓）。别墅前有开阔的庭院（铺青石板，中央设喷泉），庭院周围种着柠檬树与橄榄树，远处是连绵的托斯卡纳田野，夕阳下别墅的影子被拉得很长，静谧又典雅
英文内容: On the outskirts of Florence, the Renaissance villa sits on a hillside, with a symmetrical layout (central main building + auxiliary buildings on both sides). The outer wall is built with light yellow stone, the doors and windows are arched (with relief decorations on the arch edges), and the roof is covered with red terracotta tiles (gentle slope). In front of the villa is an open courtyard (paved with bluestone, with a fountain in the center); lemon trees and olive trees are planted around the courtyard; the rolling Tuscan fields are in the distance; the villa's shadow is stretched long at sunset, quiet and elegant

标题: 荷兰风车村建筑（赞丹风车村）
内容: 荷兰赞丹，风车村沿河岸分布，一座座风车高约 20 米（木质风叶，白色风车塔身）。风车旁是彩色木屋（红、黄、绿等明亮色彩，屋顶覆盖黑色瓦片），木屋门窗为白色（木质百叶窗）。河岸停靠着木船，村民们在屋前晾晒郁金香花束，风吹动风车叶片转动，吱呀声与河水声交织，充满荷兰风情
英文内容: In Zaanstad, the Netherlands, the windmill village is distributed along the riverbank; each windmill is about 20 meters high (wooden sails, white windmill tower). Next to the windmills are colorful wooden houses (bright colors such as red, yellow, green, with black tiles on the roof); the doors and windows of the wooden houses are white (wooden shutters). Wooden boats are moored on the riverbank; villagers dry tulip bouquets in front of the houses; the wind blows the windmill sails to rotate; the creaking sound mingles with the river sound, full of Dutch style

标题: 新古典主义政府建筑（美国国会大厦）
内容: 华盛顿市中心，新古典主义风格的国会大厦矗立在高地上，中央穹顶直径约 33 米（顶端有 “自由女神” 雕像）。外立面采用白色大理石，正面有 8 根巨大的科林斯柱（柱高约 19 米，柱头有茛苕叶装饰）。大厦前是宽阔的草坪，草坪上飘扬着美国国旗，游客们在台阶下拍照留念，阳光照耀下，白色建筑与蓝天相映，庄重又威严
英文内容: In downtown Washington D.C., the Neoclassical-style Capitol stands on a high ground, with a central dome about 33 meters in diameter (topped with a "Statue of Freedom"). The outer facade is made of white marble, and there are 8 huge Corinthian columns on the front (about 19 meters high, with acanthus leaf decorations on the capitals). In front of the building is a wide lawn, with the American flag fluttering on the lawn; tourists take photos under the steps; under the sun, the white building contrasts with the blue sky, solemn and majestic

标题: 巴洛克式宫殿（凡尔赛宫镜厅）
内容: 凡尔赛宫内，镜厅长约 73 米，两侧墙面镶嵌着 17 面巨大明镜（每面由多块镜片组成），镜面对面是 17 扇落地玻璃窗（通向花园）。天花板绘有金色与蓝色的神话壁画，廊柱为镀金铜制，地面铺白色大理石（拼接成几何图案）。阳光透过玻璃窗照进厅内，镜面反射出璀璨光芒，贵族们在此举办舞会，裙摆与水晶灯的光芒交织，奢华又浪漫
英文内容: In the Palace of Versailles, the Hall of Mirrors is about 73 meters long; 17 huge mirrors are inlaid on the walls on both sides (each composed of multiple lenses), and 17 floor-to-ceiling glass windows (leading to the garden) are opposite the mirrors. The ceiling is painted with golden and blue mythological murals, the columns are gilded copper, and the floor is paved with white marble (pieced into geometric patterns). Sunlight shines into the hall through the glass windows, and the mirrors reflect bright light; nobles hold dances here, with the light of skirts and crystal chandeliers intertwined, luxurious and romantic

标题: 匈牙利布达佩斯温泉建筑（塞切尼温泉浴场）
内容: 布达佩斯市中心，塞切尼温泉浴场是新古典主义风格，外立面用黄色石材砌筑，正面有 6 根巨大的爱奥尼柱（柱头有涡卷装饰）。建筑顶部有雕像（象征温泉与健康），窗户为拱形（玻璃上有花纹）。浴场前是广场，广场上有温泉喷泉，游客们穿着浴袍在建筑前散步，蒸汽从浴场窗户冒出，充满休闲氛围
英文内容: In downtown Budapest, Széchenyi Thermal Bath is in Neoclassical style; the outer facade is built with yellow stone, with 6 huge Ionic

标题: 意大利广场建筑（罗马西班牙广场）
内容: 罗马市中心，西班牙广场由阶梯与建筑群组成，广场中央有巴洛克式喷泉（“破船喷泉”，石雕船身半浸在水中）。阶梯共 137 级（宽约 28 米，铺灰色石材），阶梯两侧是咖啡馆与商铺（建筑为浅黄色，门窗有拱形装饰）。游客们坐在阶梯上休息，鸽子在广场上飞舞，傍晚时分，夕阳为建筑镀上金边，街头艺人弹奏着吉他，充满生活气息
英文内容: In downtown Rome, the Spanish Steps consist of stairs and buildings; a Baroque fountain ("Fontana della Barcaccia," with a stone-carved ship hull half-submerged in water) is in the center. The stairs have 137 steps (about 28 meters wide, paved with gray stone); cafes and shops are on both sides of the stairs (light yellow buildings with arched decorations on doors and windows). Tourists sit on the stairs to rest; pigeons fly in the square; in the evening, the setting sun gilds the buildings; street artists play the guitar, full of life

标题: 奥地利阿尔卑斯山木屋（因斯布鲁克木屋）
内容: 奥地利因斯布鲁克郊外，阿尔卑斯山木屋由原木搭建（深棕色木材，树皮纹理清晰），屋顶覆盖厚重的木瓦（坡度陡，防止积雪）。木屋外墙挂着干柴与登山装备，门窗为白色（窗框有花纹雕刻）。木屋周围是积雪覆盖的山坡，门前有木梯通向雪地，冬季时屋内暖光透出，烟囱冒出白烟，与白雪相映，温馨又静谧
英文内容: On the outskirts of Innsbruck, Austria, the Alpine wooden house is built with logs (dark brown wood, clear bark texture), and the roof is covered with thick wooden shingles (steep slope to prevent snow accumulation). Dried firewood and mountaineering equipment are hung on the outer wall; the doors and windows are white (carved patterns on the window frames). The wooden house is surrounded by snow-covered hillsides; a wooden ladder leads from the door to the snow; warm light shines out of the house in winter; white smoke rises from the chimney, contrasting with the snow, warm and quiet

内容: 藤蔓细长（可缠绕树木生长），叶片呈心形（翠绿带金边），开淡紫色小花（花芯为红色，似红豆），若一对恋人分别触碰藤蔓，花朵会同时绽放，象征 “相思相通”，多生长在恋人常去的山谷

内容: 全株洁白透明（似冰晶质感），无叶绿素（靠吸收腐殖质生长），花型呈钟状（顶端下垂），生长在深山腐叶堆中，阴天会散发微弱白光，民间认为是 “幽灵的指引花”
英文内容: Entire plant white and transparent (crystal-like texture); no chlorophyll (grows by absorbing humus); bell-shaped flowers (drooping at the top); grows in deep mountain humus piles; emits faint white light on cloudy days; traditionally regarded as the guiding flower of ghosts

内容: 株高约半米，叶片呈淡绿色披针形，花瓣为柔粉色（边缘泛微光），花开时散发清甜香气，闻者会忘却忧愁（但会短暂失忆），多生长在仙境溪边，晨露滋润后药效更强
英文内容: About 0.5 meters tall, with light green lanceolate leaves and soft pink petals (faint glow on edges); emits sweet fragrance when blooming—smellers forget sorrows (but suffer short-term amnesia); mostly grows by fairyland streams, with stronger efficacy after being moistened by morning dew

内容: 藤蔓攀援生长，叶片呈长卵形（深绿色，表面有光泽），花朵为白色喇叭状（直径约 15 厘米），仅在满月夜绽放，花瓣反射月光呈银白色，花香能安抚狂暴生物，生长在月光充足的山坡
英文内容: Climbing vines; long oval dark green leaves (shiny surface); white trumpet-shaped flowers (about 15 cm in diameter); only blooms on full-moon nights; petals reflect moonlight to appear silvery-white; fragrance calms violent creatures; grows on slopes with sufficient moonlight

内容: 无根系（靠空气浮力漂浮），茎秆细长（淡绿色，中空），叶片呈羽毛状（白色，轻盈如棉絮），常成片漂浮在魔法云层下方，触碰会产生微弱浮力（可让人短暂离地），风吹过时会随风飘动并发出清脆声响
英文内容: No roots (floats by air buoyancy); slender light green hollow stems; feather-like white leaves (light as cotton); often floats in clusters under magic clouds; touching it produces weak buoyancy (allows people to leave the ground briefly); makes crisp sounds when blown by wind

内容: 花茎纤细（约 30 厘米），叶片呈椭圆形（随花期变色：春绿、夏蓝、秋黄、冬红），花朵可随周围环境颜色变换（如遇红色物体变粉，遇蓝色物体变紫），生长在魔法森林，花瓣研磨后可制作隐身颜料
英文内容: Slender stems (about 30 cm); oval leaves (color changes with seasons: green in spring, blue in summer, yellow in autumn, red in winter); flowers change color with surrounding environment (e.g., pink near red objects, purple near blue objects); grows in magic forests; petals can be ground to make invisibility pigment

内容: 株高约 60 厘米，叶片呈心形（深绿色，手感温暖），花朵为橙黄色（似小太阳，花瓣向外展开），即使在寒冬也能绽放，周围 2 米内温度会升高 5-10℃，生长在寒冷的北方雪原，是冬季生物的 “取暖站”
英文内容: About 60 cm tall; heart-shaped dark green leaves (warm to the touch); orange-yellow sun-like flowers (petals spread outward); blooms even in severe winter; temperature within 2 meters rises by 5-10℃; grows in cold northern snowfields; warmth station for winter creatures
