sketch rendering style {prompt}. Monochromatic (usually black and white) drawing with varying line weights to indicate shading, depth, and form. The lines can be rough or smooth, and the overall effect is like a traditional pencil or charcoal sketch, such as a sketch of a still - life with objects defined by lines and areas of shaded tones
graffiti style {prompt} . street art, vibrant, urban, detailed, tag, mural

pastel rendering style {prompt}. Soft, powdery - looking colors that blend gently. The colors have a slightly muted and warm quality, and the surface may have a slightly grainy texture due to the nature of pastels. A portrait in pastel might have a soft, almost hazy look to the skin
Pencil Sketch Drawing, {prompt}, black and white drawing, graphite drawing

cartoon rendering style {prompt}. Vivid, bold - colored characters with exaggerated features such as large eyes for expressiveness, and simple, clean - cut shapes for bodies. The backgrounds are often simplified and filled with bright, flat colors, like in a classic Disney or Pixar - style cartoon
Colored Pencil Art, {prompt}, colored pencil strokes, light color, visible paper texture, colored pencil art
Color Field Painting, {prompt}, abstract, simple, geometic, color field painting style
Dripping Paint Splatter Art, {prompt}, dramatic, paint drips, splatters, dripping paint

cyberpunk rendering style {prompt}. A combination of dark, gritty elements with bright, neon - like lights. The scene may include high - tech, futuristic buildings with digital billboards, flying vehicles, and a lot of chrome and metal textures. The overall atmosphere is of a high - tech, dystopian future

ink wash rendering style {prompt}. Fluid, black - and - white (or sometimes with a touch of color) strokes that create a sense of movement and depth. The ink spreads and blends on the paper, similar to traditional Chinese ink paintings of landscapes or calligraphy. The effect is often elegant and has a strong cultural aesthetic

3D rendering style {prompt}. Objects have a clear three - dimensional form, with accurate perspective, lighting, and shading. You can clearly see the depth and volume of each element, such as a 3D - rendered car with realistic reflections on its body and well - defined shadows underneath

oil painting rendering style {prompt}. Rich, thickly applied colors with visible impasto texture, giving the image a three - dimensional feel. The blending of colors creates depth, similar to famous oil paintings like those of Leonardo da Vinci or Rembrandt. Brushstrokes contribute to the overall texture and mood of the piece

neon rendering style {prompt}. Glowing, highly saturated colors that mimic the look of neon lights. The colors often have a strong, electric - like quality, and there may be a halo or glow effect around the lit elements. Ideal for creating a cyberpunk or nightlife - themed scene
play-doh style {prompt} . sculpture, clay art, centered composition, Claymation

watercolor rendering style {prompt}. Soft, flowing colors that blend and bleed into each other, creating a dreamy effect. Brushstrokes are visible, adding an organic touch. For example, a landscape with watercolor - rendered trees would have leaves with a soft, diffused look as if painted with wet pigments
Double Exposure Style, {prompt}, double image ghost effect, image combination, double exposure style

photorealistic rendering style {prompt}. Exceptionally detailed portrayal of every element, be it the texture of a leather couch down to the individual creases and grain, or the play of light on a glass vase with accurate refractions and highlights. The colors match real - world counterparts precisely, and shadows are cast in a way that mimics real - life lighting conditions
Japanese Ink Drawing, {prompt}, ink drawing, inkwash, Japanese Ink Drawing
Blueprint Schematic Drawing, {prompt}, technical drawing, blueprint, schematic

内容: 园林假山顶上，小巧的望江亭（四角方亭）矗立，亭身呈浅灰色，亭柱挂着蓝底白字楹联，亭周点缀着迎春、迎春，假山脚下有小瀑布流进池塘，游人登亭可俯瞰全园，云雾缭绕时，亭似浮在山间的仙阁
英文内容: On top of the garden rockery, a small four-cornered pavilion stands; light gray pavilion body, blue-and-white couplets hang on pillars; winter jasmine and rhododendrons are dotted around; a small waterfall at the rockery foot flows into the pond; visitors climb to overlook the whole garden; when mist shrouds, the pavilion seems like a fairy pavilion floating in mountains

内容: 牡丹园中央的圆形攒尖顶圆亭，亭柱为朱红色，亭顶覆粉色琉璃瓦（顶心有金色宝顶），亭内摆着雕花木凳，亭周牡丹盛开（红、粉、白各色），游人坐在亭中，如置身花海中央，春风拂过花瓣飘落，唯美又浪漫
英文内容: In the center of the peony garden, the round spire pavilion has vermilion pillars; pink glazed tiles on the roof (with a golden treasure top); carved wooden stools inside; peonies bloom around (red, pink, white); visitors sit as if in the center of a flower sea; petals fall in the spring breeze, beautiful and romantic

内容: 湖边的三层水阁，木质结构呈深棕色，一层一半在水中（用石柱支撑），二三层有雕花栏杆，阁顶覆青瓦，阁前有石阶通向湖面，游人登阁可赏湖景，夜晚阁内点灯，灯光映在湖中，与星光交相辉映，浪漫又静谧
英文内容: By the lake, the three-story waterside pavilion has a dark brown wooden structure; half of the first floor is over the water (supported by stone pillars), carved railings on the second and third floors; green tiles on the roof; stone steps lead to the lake in front; visitors climb to enjoy the lake view; lights are lit in the pavilion at night, reflecting in the lake, shining with starlight, romantic and quiet

内容: 荷塘边的水榭，木质结构呈浅棕色，榭身一半架在水面上，底部用石柱支撑，榭檐下挂着红灯笼，榭内摆着雕花木椅，游人坐在榭中可赏荷叶荷花，雨后水面泛起涟漪，榭影随波晃动，清新又灵动
英文内容: By the lotus pond, the waterside pavilion has a light brown wooden structure; half of it is built over the water, supported by stone pillars; red lanterns hang under the eaves; carved wooden chairs are placed inside; visitors sit to enjoy lotus leaves and flowers; ripples spread on the water after rain, the pavilion's shadow sways with waves, fresh and agile

内容: 园林古树下的碑亭，亭身小巧（六角形），青灰砖石结构，亭内立着青石碑（碑刻古文），碑旁摆着石香炉，亭周种着侧柏，古树枝桠伸向亭顶，阳光透过枝叶洒在石碑上，形成斑驳光影，营造出古朴肃穆的氛围
英文内容: Under the ancient garden tree, the stele pavilion is small (hexagonal), with a gray brick structure; a green stone stele (with ancient texts) stands inside, a stone incense burner beside it; arborvitae grow around; ancient tree branches stretch to the pavilion top; sunlight filters through leaves onto the stele, creating dappled light, a solemn and ancient atmosphere

内容: 荷花池上的廊桥，桥身用青石板砌成，桥上建木质廊屋（廊柱浅棕，廊顶青瓦），廊屋两侧有长椅，游人走在廊桥上，可避雨遮阳，低头能赏池中荷花，抬头可见蓝天白云，廊桥影子映在池中，与荷花相映成趣
英文内容: Over the lotus pond, the covered bridge has a bluestone body; a wooden corridor (light brown pillars, green tiles) is built on it; benches on both sides of the corridor; visitors walk to shelter from rain and sun; look down to enjoy lotus flowers, look up to see blue sky and white clouds; the bridge's shadow in the pond contrasts with lotus flowers, interesting and charming

内容: 庭院入口处的垂花门，门框为朱红色，门楣两侧垂着雕花木质 “垂莲柱”（似莲花含苞），门内是青石板庭院，院中有石榴树，门外种着月季，花开时节，红花映衬朱门，游人进门时如踏入雅致秘境
英文内容: At the courtyard entrance, the pendant flower gate has a vermilion frame; carved wooden "lotus pendant pillars" (like budding lotus) hang on both sides of the lintel; a bluestone courtyard is inside, with a pomegranate tree; roses grow outside; when flowers bloom, red flowers contrast with the vermilion gate; visitors enter as if stepping into an elegant secret place

内容: 园林角落的二层藏经阁，木质结构呈深棕色，一层有朱红大门（门雕麒麟纹），二层有镂空花窗，阁顶覆青瓦（屋脊有吻兽装饰），阁前种着古松，松影映在阁壁上，夕阳西下时，余晖为阁楼镀上金边，庄重又古朴
英文内容: In the garden corner, the two-story scripture-storing pavilion has a dark brown wooden structure; a vermilion door (with unicorn carvings) on the first floor, hollowed flower windows on the second; green tiles on the roof (with mythical beast decorations on the ridge); an ancient pine grows in front; the pine's shadow falls on the pavilion wall; at sunset, the setting sun gilds the pavilion, solemn and ancient

内容: 园林中央的花厅，木质结构呈浅棕色，厅身四面敞开（无墙，仅用圆柱支撑），厅顶覆青瓦，厅内摆着雕花长桌（铺淡蓝桌布），厅周种着四季花卉（春兰、夏荷、秋菊、冬梅），四季皆有花赏，游人在厅中可品茶赏花，雅致又舒适
英文内容: In the garden center, the flower hall has a light brown wooden structure; open on all four sides (no walls, only supported by columns); green tiles on the roof; a carved long table (covered with light blue tablecloth) inside; flowers of four seasons (spring orchid, summer lotus, autumn chrysanthemum, winter plum) grow around; flowers can be enjoyed in all seasons; visitors taste tea and enjoy flowers, elegant and comfortable

内容: 园林墙边，曲廊蜿蜒延伸，廊柱为浅灰色，廊顶覆青瓦，廊壁上嵌着圆形、扇形等各式花窗（窗棂雕缠枝莲纹），廊外种着粉白海棠，花瓣偶尔飘进廊内，游人漫步廊中，透过花窗可赏园景，步移景异
英文内容: Along the garden wall, the winding corridor stretches; light gray corridor pillars, green tiles on the roof; various flower windows (round, fan-shaped, with lotus vine carvings on lattice) are inlaid on the corridor wall; pink-white crabapples grow outside; petals occasionally drift into the corridor; visitors stroll inside, enjoying garden scenery through windows, with views changing at every step

内容: 假山半山腰的观景台，台面用青石板铺成，台边有汉白玉栏杆（雕缠枝纹），台上摆着青铜香炉，游人站在台上，可俯瞰园林全景，云雾弥漫时，台似浮在云端，远处亭台楼阁若隐若现，如仙境一般
英文内容: On the hillside of the rockery, the viewing platform is paved with bluestone slabs; white marble railings (with vine carvings) on the edge; a bronze incense burner on it; visitors stand to overlook the whole garden; when mist fills the air, the platform seems to float in clouds; pavilions and towers in the distance loom, like a fairyland

内容: 园林小溪上，青灰色拱券小石桥横跨，桥面铺着青石板（有细碎纹路），桥两侧有矮石栏（栏板雕云纹），桥下溪水潺潺，溪底有鹅卵石，桥边种着鸢尾花，游人过桥时，可听水声赏花香，桥影映在溪中如弯月
英文内容: Over the garden stream, a gray arched stone bridge spans; bluestone slabs (with fine lines) pave the deck; low stone railings (with cloud carvings on boards) on both sides; the stream gurgles under the bridge, with pebbles at the bottom; irises grow by the bridge; visitors cross to listen to the stream and enjoy the fragrance; the bridge's shadow in the stream is like a crescent moon

内容: 园林分区处，月洞门呈圆形，门框为青灰色砖石砌成，门楣上刻 “邀月” 二字，门内是成片竹林，门外种着几株红枫，游人穿过门时，竹林与红枫形成框景，月光洒进门洞时，如一轮圆月嵌在园墙上
英文内容: At the garden partition, the moon gate is round, with a gray brick frame; "Inviting the Moon" is carved on the lintel; a bamboo forest is inside the gate, several red maples grow outside; when visitors pass through, bamboo and maples form a framed scene; when moonlight shines through, it looks like a full moon inlaid on the garden wall

内容: 湖边的画舫斋，整体呈船形，木质船体涂成棕红色，船身两侧有雕花窗棂，船头挂着黄色绸帘，船内摆着古琴与书画，游人坐在斋中，如乘舟游湖，岸边柳树垂到船边，微风拂过绸帘飘动，雅致如古画
英文内容: By the lake, the boat-shaped study is in a ship form; the wooden hull is reddish-brown, carved lattice windows on both sides; yellow silk curtains hang at the bow; a guqin, calligraphy and paintings are placed inside; visitors sit as if boating on the lake; willow branches hang to the boat side; silk curtains flutter in the breeze, elegant as an ancient painting

内容: 竹林旁的扇形轩，轩身呈扇形，木质框架涂浅黄，轩顶覆竹瓦，轩内摆着竹制桌椅，轩外竹影婆娑，风穿竹林时，竹声沙沙，游人坐在轩中，可赏竹景听竹声，雨后竹叶带水珠，光影透过竹叶洒进轩内，清新雅致
英文内容: By the bamboo forest, the fan-shaped veranda is in a fan form; light yellow wooden frame, bamboo tiles on the roof; bamboo tables and chairs inside; bamboo shadows sway outside; when wind blows through bamboo, it rustles; visitors sit to enjoy bamboo scenery and listen to the sound; after rain, bamboo leaves have water droplets; light filters through leaves into the veranda, fresh and elegant

内容: 园林墙边的半亭，一半依墙（青灰砖墙），一半向外敞开，亭顶为攒尖顶（覆青瓦），亭柱挂着浅紫色纱帘，亭外种着紫藤，紫藤花垂到亭内，游人坐在亭中，可赏墙外竹景，闻紫藤花香，午后阳光照进亭内，温暖又惬意
英文内容: By the garden wall, the half-pavilion is half against the wall (gray brick wall), half open outward; a spire roof (with green tiles); light purple silk curtains hang on pillars; wisteria grows outside, its flowers hanging into the pavilion; visitors sit to enjoy bamboo scenery outside the wall and smell wisteria fragrance; afternoon sunlight shines in, warm and comfortable

内容: 园林湖泊中央，八角攒尖顶湖心亭矗立，朱红立柱配青灰瓦檐，亭檐下挂着淡青色风铃，亭内摆着汉白玉石桌石凳，湖面倒映亭影，荷叶环绕亭基，微风拂过风铃轻响，如漂浮在碧波上的雅致画框
英文内容: In the center of the garden lake, an octagonal spire 湖心亭 stands; vermilion pillars match gray tile eaves, light cyan wind chimes hang under the eaves; white marble tables and stools are placed inside; the pavilion's shadow is reflected on the lake, lotus leaves surround its base; wind chimes tinkle in the breeze, like an elegant frame floating on blue waves

内容: 草坪中央的四角攒尖顶方亭，亭柱为浅灰色，亭顶覆青瓦（顶心有宝顶装饰），亭内石桌刻围棋棋盘，亭周种着牡丹与芍药，花开时节，花海围绕方亭，游人可在亭中对弈赏景，微风拂过花香袭人，惬意又雅致
英文内容: In the center of the lawn, the four-cornered spire square pavilion has light gray pillars; green tiles on the roof (with a treasure top decoration); a stone table with a go board inside; peonies and paeonies grow around; when flowers bloom, the pavilion is surrounded by a sea of flowers; visitors play go and enjoy scenery; the fragrance hits the nose in the breeze, comfortable and elegant

内容: 湖边的石舫（不系舟），船体用青石雕琢（呈浅灰色，刻水波纹），船上建木质亭榭（亭顶青瓦，亭柱浅棕），亭内摆着红木桌椅，船身周围种着芦苇，微风拂过芦苇晃动，石舫似在碧波中缓缓航行，古朴又灵动
英文内容: By the lake, the stone boat (unmoored boat) is carved from green stone (light gray, with wave carvings); a wooden pavilion (green tiles, light brown pillars) is built on it; red wooden tables and chairs inside; reeds grow around the boat; reeds sway in the breeze; the stone boat seems to sail slowly on blue waves, ancient and agile

内容: 园林外围的雕花砖墙，墙身呈青灰色，墙顶覆青瓦（有滴水瓦当），墙面嵌着各式雕花砖（牡丹、荷花、梅花图案），墙内种着爬墙虎，藤蔓爬满墙面，开花时墙面上点缀着淡紫色小花，墙外人行道旁种着银杏，秋叶落在墙边，古朴又有生机
英文内容: Around the garden, the carved brick wall is gray; green tiles on the top (with drip tiles); various carved bricks (peony, lotus, plum patterns) are inlaid on the wall; ivy grows inside, its vines covering the wall; light purple flowers dot the wall when blooming; ginkgoes grow outside the wall by the sidewalk; autumn leaves fall beside the wall, ancient and vibrant

内容: 视频展示一段鱼眼镜头下的视频画面，镜头采用鱼眼视角，带来了一种独特的弯曲效果，将繁忙的城市街道呈现得更加引人注目。画面的宽阔视野让观众感受到建筑物仿佛在向天空倾斜，街道两旁的高楼在鱼眼镜头的渲染下，显得分外壮观而立体，扭曲的线条形成强烈的视觉冲击，充分展现了城市的活力与喧嚣。
视频中，镜头中景展示一位古风女子袅袅婷婷地走在花丛中，长裙随风飘荡，仿佛在与自然交融。
赛车缓慢移动，背景在静谧中逐渐清晰，一切都仿佛被时间拉长。车速温和，带来一种悠然自得的体验与心灵的宁静，车手在这片安详中如同与周围的环境融为一体，流露出的专注让人心生敬畏。
视频中展示了一块立方体石块，镜头聚焦在立方体石块上，阳光透过，散发出温暖的光泽。随着镜头轻轻移动，石块的细节在视野中渐渐变化，周围环境模糊成背景。随即，镜头自然地切换到旁边的立方体铁块，光滑的金属表面在阳光下闪烁。焦点流畅地转移，铁块的冷冽与石块的厚重形成鲜明对比。镜头在两者之间游走，展现出各自的独特魅力
视频展示了一片紧张的森林，狂风肆虐，猛烈地吹动着树梢和树叶，发出一阵阵低沉的沙沙声，如同大自然在低语着不安的预兆。树干摇曳，似乎在抗争着这突如其来的威严。天空中乌云密布，厚重的云层像是压抑的心情，笼罩着整个画面，透出一种阴郁而凝重的气氛。周围的一切似乎也在为即将到来的变化而屏息，整个场景充满了紧迫感，令人心头微微一紧，仿佛随时都会爆发出无法预知的风暴，使人感受到大自然的无情与力量。
视频展示了植物以延时效果迅速生长开花的惊人过程。画面中，嫩芽在短短几秒钟内经历了生长与绽放，从青涩的芽苞到鲜艳的花朵，瞬间令观众目眩神迷。每个环节都被清晰地捕捉，展现出生命力的蓬勃与美丽，让人不禁感叹自然界的奇妙与神奇。
视频中展示了一块巨大的立方体石块，稳稳伫立在广场中央。镜头缓缓拉远，石块的宏伟轮廓逐渐显现，广场的石砖和周围的草坪逐渐展露。最终，整个广场的景色展现在眼前。
人流缓缓移动，慢动作放大了每个行人的步伐，行人与环境融为一体，映衬出生活的每一个细节。步伐缓慢却充满韵律，仿佛在诉说着城市的故事，带着思考与感悟，分享着生活的诗意。
视频中，镜头远景展示了繁华的城市街道，宽阔的人行道上人来人往，形成了一个生动而热闹的画面。
视频中展示了一块巨大的立方体石块，伫立在广场中央，周围宁静。镜头缓缓推进，逐渐靠近石块，粗犷的纹理和岁月的痕迹逐渐清晰。
梵高的《星夜》中，一位穿着现代服饰的滑板少年在扭曲的树木间穿梭，星空下的光影效果与滑板的轨迹交相辉映。
视频展示了一片孤独的森林，四周寂静无声，仿佛时间在这一刻停滞。树叶轻轻飘落，缓缓地铺洒在地面上，发出微弱的窸窣声，仿佛在低声诉说着秋天的离别。空旷的空间中只有风声孤独地回荡，似乎在唤醒这片沉寂的土地。阴影在树木间交错，营造出冷清而忧郁的氛围，整个场景透着一丝孤寂，让人感受到一种淡淡的惆怅，仿佛在向失去的时光致敬，身处于这一片宁静中，让人不禁沉思。
视频展示了一个人物在厨房环境中的生动场景，特别的是，这个人物是由毛毡制成的，增添了几分童趣。毛毡小人正站在一个迷你厨房里，手里拿着小锅铲，仿佛在精心烹饪美食。背景是一面挂满各种厨具的墙，整个空间充满了温馨的气氛。视频通过固定视角捕捉了毛毡小人的每一个动作，包括搅拌、翻炒等，展现了其精湛的 “厨艺”。
视频中展示了一个立方体石块在广场中央滚动，镜头跟随运动。随着砾石的移动，周围的绿草如茵。镜头灵活地紧贴着砾石，捕捉到地面上细微的纹路和春风掠过的动感。
视频中，镜头近景显示一位古风女子捧着一把青色折扇，指尖轻轻划过扇面上的精美花纹，仿佛在细细品味其中的韵味。
视频展示了一片幽深的森林，夜晚的宁静如同一层柔和的轻纱，温柔地笼罩着每一寸土地。四周静谧无声，仿佛时间在此刻凝固，唯有微风轻轻拂过树梢，带来细微的沙沙声，仿佛在与大自然低语。夜空如深蓝的绒布，星光点点闪烁，宛如遥远的宝石镶嵌其中，散发出清冷而柔和的光芒。整个场景显得安静而和谐，令人心旷神怡，仿佛走入了一个梦幻般的境地，恍若与世隔绝，尽情融入这片自然的怀抱。
视频中，镜头特写一位古风女子的脸庞，柔和的光线洒在她的皮肤上，勾勒出细腻的轮廓。

视频展示了一片庄严的森林，树木高大挺拔，如同守护者般屹立在大地上，散发出一种无言的力量。阳光透过浓密的树梢，洒下斑驳的光芒，形成了层层光影在地面交织，仿佛在绘制一幅自然的画卷。空气中弥漫着清新的气息，偶尔传来的鸟鸣声低沉而庄重，增添了几分肃穆的氛围。整个场景透着一种宏伟与宁静，引人肃然起敬。这个森林仿佛是时光的见证，承载着无数故事与秘密，让人感受到大自然的庄重与神秘，令人心生敬畏，仿佛置身于一片灵性之地。
视频开始时，镜头采用 FPV（第一人视角）无人机拍摄，带来了一种身临其境的感受。镜头迅速穿越城市的高楼大厦之间，展现出宏伟的都市景观。建筑物在视野中迅速闪过，光影交错，映衬出城市的现代与繁华。
穿越少女，在古代宫廷中烛光照耀下学习礼仪一举一动皆显古风优雅。
一个人站在游戏风格的像素世界里，配备有史以来最华丽、高分辨率 8K 纹理包。
法庭上，一只机智敏捷、口才了得的狐狸律师，身着笔挺的律师袍，正滔滔不绝地为当事人辩护，她的每一个论点都精准有力，让旁听者无不为之动容，勾线动画。
视频展示了废土风格背景下，一位仿佛来自异世界的飞天仙女的惊艳现身。她身着破旧却华丽的服饰，背后展开一对由废墟碎片构成的奇异翅膀，翱翔在荒凉的地景之上。镜头跟随她的飞行轨迹，从低空拉高至广阔的天空，展现出她轻盈的身姿与废土世界的强烈对比，每一次挥翅都似乎在诉说着生存与希望的故事。
视频展示了一个在末世中行走的人的场景，镜头从高处俯拍一个人在废土风格的场景中随着阳光缓缓前行。
闪烁的霓虹灯下一名身着皮夹克的赛博战士在废弃的电子工厂中穿行镜头从他的背影拉远展示出一个充满未来科技感的城市夜景。
视频以广角镜头捕捉一个繁忙的城市街道监控场景，画面宽广，视野开阔。街道两旁高楼林立，车流不息，行人川流不息，展现出城市生活的喧嚣与活力。
视频展示了一片充满活力的森林，阳光透过树冠洒下金色的光斑，鸟儿在林间欢快地飞舞，清脆的鸣叫声在空中回荡，仿佛在为这片生机勃勃的天地演唱颂歌。树叶在微风中轻轻摇摆，像是随着乐曲的节拍在欢快地起舞，欣欣向荣的景象令人心生愉悦。小动物们在草地上嬉戏，花朵在阳光下绽放，整个森林充满了生机与活力，仿佛在诉说着生命的美好与无限可能，让人感受到大自然的蓬勃与希望。
视频中，镜头采用鸟瞰视角，俯瞰整个城市的全貌，展现出互相交织的街道与建筑。
赛车快速行驶，背景在瞬息之间模糊，一切都仿佛变成了色彩的交错。车速迅猛，让人感受到强烈的刺激与肾上腺素的飙升，车手在这片轰鸣中如同掌控了整个世界，释放出的激情让人热血沸腾。
视频从一双行走的腿开始，镜头采用低角度拍摄，聚焦于脚步的移动。画面中，鞋子踩踏在粗糙的废弃地面上，周围是破碎的混凝土和零散的杂草，展现出废土风格的荒凉与颓废。
视频中展示了一块巨大的立方体石块，伫立在广场中央。镜头旋转延展，围绕这块石块延伸，捕捉到表面粗犷的纹理和阳光下闪烁的细微光泽。
水平镜像对称构图, 人物站在水边, 倒影与实体完美对称, 画面梦幻超现实
英文内容: Horizontal mirror symmetry composition, character standing by the water, reflection perfectly symmetrical with the entity, dreamy and surreal frame

内容: 不对称留白构图, 一侧大量留白另一侧是密集元素, 人物在交界处, 对比强烈
英文内容: Asymmetrical negative space composition, large amount of negative space on one side and dense elements on the other, character at the junction, strong contrast

内容: 上三分之一构图, 人物头部和肩部在画面上方, 下方大量环境信息, 强调场景叙事性
英文内容: Upper third composition, character's head and shoulders in the upper part of the frame, large amount of environmental information below, emphasizing scene narrative

内容: 环绕式负空间构图, 人物四周均匀留白被孤立, 中心聚焦强, 强调孤独或独立感
英文内容: Surrounding negative space composition, character surrounded by uniform negative space and isolated, strong central focus, emphasizing loneliness or independence

内容: 极简三分构图, 人物极小位于右上交叉点, 大面积纯色背景, 突出孤独和空旷感
英文内容: Minimalist third composition, character is very small at the upper right intersection, large area of solid color background, emphasizing loneliness and emptiness

内容: 动态三分构图, 人物在左侧三分线起步奔跑, 右侧留白表现运动方向和空间, 充满动势
英文内容: Dynamic third composition, character starts running at the left third line, right negative space showing movement direction and space, full of momentum

内容: 倾斜三分构图, 画面旋转15度, 人物仍遵循三分法则, 打破常规增添活力和不安感
英文内容: Tilted third composition, frame rotated 15 degrees, character still following the rule of thirds, breaking convention and adding vitality and unease

内容: 偏移中心构图, 人物略偏离中心5-10%, 打破呆板感, 保持稳定性同时增添趣味
英文内容: Offset center composition, character slightly deviated from the center by 5-10%, breaking rigidity, maintaining stability while adding interest

内容: 多层次三分构图, 前景占下三分, 人物在中三分, 背景在上三分, 层次丰富有深度
英文内容: Multi-layer third composition, foreground occupies lower third, character in middle third, background in upper third, rich layers and depth

内容: 色彩分割构图, 画面用强烈色彩分为几块区域, 人物在色彩交界处, 现代感强烈
英文内容: Color division composition, frame divided into several areas with strong colors, character at the color junction, strong modern sense

内容: 垂直中轴对称构图, 人物居中, 左右环境完全对称(建筑/树木), 画面庄重稳定有仪式感
英文内容: Vertical axis symmetry composition, character centered, left and right environments completely symmetrical (buildings/trees), solemn and stable frame with ritual sense

内容: 黄金矩形嵌套构图, 画面由多个黄金矩形嵌套组成, 人物在最内层矩形, 视觉聚焦自然
英文内容: Golden rectangle nested composition, frame composed of multiple nested golden rectangles, character in the innermost rectangle, natural visual focus

内容: 双重对称构图, 两个人物分别位于对称轴两侧做镜像动作, 画面和谐统一富有张力
英文内容: Double symmetry composition, two characters on both sides of the symmetry axis making mirror movements, harmonious and unified frame with tension

内容: 下三分之一构图, 人物占据画面下方, 上方是开阔天空或建筑, 营造渺小感和空间感
英文内容: Lower third composition, character occupies the lower part of the frame, upper part is open sky or buildings, creating a sense of smallness and space

内容: 斐波那契网格构图, 人物关键点(眼睛/手/重心)精确落在网格交叉点, 数学美感
英文内容: Fibonacci grid composition, character's key points (eyes/hands/center of gravity) accurately fall on grid intersections, mathematical beauty

内容: 正中心特写构图, 人物面部完全居中, 眼睛在画面几何中心, 四周均衡留白, 视觉冲击力强
英文内容: Direct center close-up composition, character's face completely centered, eyes at the geometric center of the frame, balanced negative space around, strong visual impact

内容: 不完全对称构图, 基本对称但有意打破一侧平衡(如一侧加入色彩), 稳定中见变化
英文内容: Incomplete symmetry composition, basically symmetrical but intentionally breaking the balance on one side (such as adding color on one side), change within stability

内容: 严格的右侧三分之一构图, 人物位于画面右侧交叉点, 左侧大面积留白(负空间), 画面平衡舒适
英文内容: Strict right third composition, character located at the right intersection of the frame, large area of negative space on the left, balanced and comfortable

内容: 黄金比例纵向分割, 人物占据画面0.618部分, 其余0.382留白或环境, 比例完美和谐
英文内容: Golden ratio vertical division, character occupies 0.618 part of the frame, the remaining 0.382 is negative space or environment, perfect and harmonious proportion

内容: 双人三分构图, 两人分别位于左右三分线上, 中间留白形成呼吸空间, 画面平衡对称
英文内容: Two-person third composition, two people located on left and right third lines respectively, middle negative space forming breathing space, balanced and symmetrical

内容: S型曲线引导构图, 环境(河流/道路/人体)形成S曲线, 人物在曲线终点, 优雅流畅
英文内容: S-curve guide composition, environment (river/road/human body) forms an S-curve, character at the end of the curve, elegant and smooth

内容: 倾斜荷兰角构图, 画面倾斜25-45度, 人物沿对角线布局, 不安感动态感强, 适合戏剧场景
英文内容: Tilted Dutch angle composition, frame tilted 25-45 degrees, character arranged along the diagonal, strong sense of unease and dynamics, suitable for dramatic scenes

内容: 光影引导线构图, 光线形成明暗分界线指向人物面部, 光影对比强烈戏剧化
英文内容: Light and shadow guide line composition, light forms a light-dark boundary line pointing to the character's face, strong dramatic light-dark contrast

内容: 道路引导线构图, 道路从前景延伸至人物位置, 自然引导视线, 纵深感强故事性丰富
英文内容: Road guide line composition, road extends from the foreground to the character's position, naturally guiding the line of sight, strong sense of depth and rich storytelling

内容: 左侧三分之一构图, 人物眼睛位于左上交叉点, 右侧留白用于文字或视觉延伸, 商业感强
英文内容: Left third composition, character's eyes at the upper left intersection, right negative space for text or visual extension, strong commercial sense

内容: 栏杆引导线构图, 栏杆/扶手从画面一侧延伸指向人物, 线条流畅引导明确
英文内容: Railing guide line composition, railings/handrails extend from one side of the frame to point to the character, smooth lines with clear guidance

内容: 交叉对角线构图, 人物位于两条对角线交点, 环境沿对角线延伸, 视觉汇聚感强
英文内容: Cross diagonal composition, character located at the intersection of two diagonals, environment extends along the diagonals, strong visual convergence

内容: 强对角线构图, 人物身体沿左下到右上对角线布局, 充满动势和张力, 打破平静
英文内容: Strong diagonal composition, character's body arranged along the diagonal from bottom-left to top-right, full of momentum and tension, breaking calmness

内容: 黄金三角构图, 对角线分割画面形成三角, 人物位于主三角区域, 次三角是环境, 动态平衡
英文内容: Golden triangle composition, frame divided by diagonals to form triangles, character in the main triangle area, secondary triangles as environment, dynamic balance

内容: 黄金螺旋构图, 人物眼睛位于螺旋中心点, 身体沿螺旋曲线延伸, 引导视线自然流动
英文内容: Golden spiral composition, character's eyes at the spiral center point, body extending along the spiral curve, guiding natural flow of sight

内容: 放射状对称构图, 人物位于圆形或多边形空间中心, 环境向四周放射, 视觉聚焦强烈
英文内容: Radial symmetry composition, character located in the center of a circular or polygonal space, environment radiating around, strong visual focus

内容: 螺旋中心构图, 环境元素呈螺旋状围绕人物中心旋转, 引导视线层层深入到人物
英文内容: Spiral center composition, environmental elements rotate in a spiral around the character center, guiding the line of sight to the character layer by layer

内容: 人群视线引导构图, 前景人物的目光和身体朝向引导至主体人物, 叙事性强
英文内容: Crowd sight guidance composition, the gaze and body orientation of foreground characters guide to the main character, strong narrative
Increases the difference between light and dark areas, making bright parts brighter and dark parts darker, enhancing the overall visual impact.
Adjusts the color temperature to add more red - orange hues, making the light feel warmer and cozier.
Simulates a misty effect, diffusing the light and reducing its clarity, creating a hazy, atmospheric look.
Applies a color scheme reminiscent of old - fashioned photography, often with warm, muted tones and a slightly faded look.
Softens the light, creating a gentle halo effect around bright areas, making the overall light look more diffused and dreamy.
Enhances the edges and details within the light, making them appear crisper and more defined.
Blurs the light, making the overall appearance less sharp and more blurred, which can be used to create a sense of motion or to soften the look.
Creates a smooth transition from one light effect to another, for example, gradually changing from a warm tone to a cool tone or from a bright to a dimmer light.
Selectively filters out certain polarized light components, reducing glare and reflections, and often enhancing color saturation in the remaining light.
Adds star - shaped streaks or rays to bright light sources, making them look like stars, especially effective for point - source lights.
Darkens the edges of the light area, drawing the viewer's attention to the center, and adding a sense of focus and depth.
Inverts the light and color values, similar to the negative of a film, resulting in a reversed color and light pattern.
Distorts the light in a circular, wide - angle way, creating a fisheye - lens - like effect with exaggerated perspective.
Shifts the color temperature towards the blue - green spectrum, giving the light a cooler, more subdued appearance.
Reduces the intensity of colors in the light, making them more muted and less vivid, resulting in a more subdued color palette.
Reduces the number of color tones in the light, creating a more graphic, poster - like effect with distinct color bands.
Boosts the saturation of all colors in the light, making them more vibrant and eye - catching.
Adds texture and color effects to mimic the look of an old, aged photograph, including yellowing, scratches, and a faded light appearance.
Simulates the look of a watercolor painting, with soft, blended colors and a fluid, artistic light effect.
Transforms the light effect to resemble a hand - drawn sketch, with simplified shapes and a more artistic, graphic look.

内容: 透视缩短效果风格。物体在图像中看起来被压缩或扭曲，模仿了当物体靠近相机时的透视视觉效果，强调了深度并创造了一种三维感。
英文内容: foreshortening effect style . Objects appear compressed or distorted in a way that mimics the visual effect of perspective when an object is close to the camera, emphasizing depth and creating a sense of three - dimensionality

内容: 全息效果拍摄风格。图像看起来具有三维悬浮感，具有彩虹般的光泽和透明感，模仿全息效果。
英文内容: hologram effect shot style . An image that appears to have a three - dimensional, floating quality, with a characteristic rainbow - like sheen and a sense of transparency, mimicking a hologram

内容: 褐色调拍摄风格。图像带有温暖的棕黄色调，类似老式照片，给人一种怀旧和经典的感觉。
英文内容: sepia tone shot style . The image has a warm, brownish - yellow tint, similar to old - fashioned photographs, giving it a nostalgic and classic look

内容: 多重曝光风格。通过重叠曝光将多张图像组合在一起，创造出复杂且层次分明的视觉构图，不同曝光的元素相互作用。
英文内容: multiple exposure style . Multiple images are combined through overlapping exposures, creating a complex and layered visual composition, with elements from different exposures interacting

内容: 镜头光晕风格。图像中出现明亮的星形或条纹状光晕，这是由于光线在镜头内部反射造成的，通常会为画面增添戏剧性或电影感，特别是当光源存在时。
英文内容: lens flare style . Bright, star - shaped or streaked flares in the image, caused by light reflecting within the lens, often adding a dramatic or cinematic look, especially when light sources are present

内容: 衍射光锥风格。从图像中的明亮光源辐射出尖锐的、星星状的光锥，这是由镜头中的衍射造成的，为图像添加了戏剧性和装饰性元素。
英文内容: diffraction spikes style . Pointed, star - like spikes radiating from bright light sources in the image, caused by diffraction in the lens, adding a dramatic and decorative element

内容: 柔和焦点拍摄风格。图像整体柔和，边缘和细节略有模糊，创造出浪漫和梦幻的氛围。
英文内容: soft focus shot style . The image has a gentle, overall softness, with edges and details slightly blurred, creating a romantic and dreamy atmosphere

内容: 过曝拍摄风格。图像比正常情况下更亮，高光细节可能会丢失，造成洗白或高调的效果。
英文内容: overexposed shot style . The image is brighter than normal, with details in the highlights potentially being lost, creating a washed - out or high - key look

内容: 失焦风格。图像中的主体或部分被故意模糊，营造出动感、柔和感，或吸引人们对其他聚焦元素的注意
英文内容: defocused style . The subject or parts of the image are intentionally blurred, creating a sense of motion, softness, or to draw attention to other focused elements

内容: 故障风格拍摄风格。图像中出现随机的、扭曲的、看起来破碎的元素，如色彩偏移、像素化和线条断裂，模仿了数字故障或错误。
英文内容: glitch style shot style . Random, distorted, and broken - looking elements in the image, such as color shifts, pixelation, and disrupted lines, mimicking a digital glitch or error

内容: 分色风格。色调范围的不同部分（阴影、中间调、高光）应用了不同的颜色，创造出富有创意和独特色彩分级效果
英文内容: split tone style . Different parts of the tonal range (shadows, midtones, highlights) have different colors applied, creating a creative and distinct color grading effect

内容: 色差风格。物体边缘可见彩色边缘，通常为红、绿、蓝色，由镜头无法将所有颜色聚焦在同一点上造成，增添了一种独特且略带扭曲的外观
英文内容: chromatic aberration style . Visible color fringing around the edges of objects, usually in red, green, and blue, caused by the lens's inability to focus all colors at the same point, adding a unique, slightly distorted look

内容: 运动模糊风格。图像中移动的物体显示出模糊效果，表明它们在曝光时间内的移动，增加了动态感和速度感。
英文内容: motion blur style . Moving objects in the image show a blurred effect, indicating their movement during the exposure time, adding a sense of dynamism and speed

内容: 锡版照相风格。一种具有独特、轻微颗粒质感和金属般表面的单色图像，具有锡版摄影的特征，给人一种老式和乡村的感觉
英文内容: tintype shot style . A monochromatic image with a distinct, slightly grainy texture and a metallic - like finish, characteristic of tintype photography, giving it an old - fashioned and rustic feel

内容: 长曝光拍摄风格。由于长时间曝光，移动的物体看起来模糊或有拖尾效果，例如流动的水看起来平滑或汽车灯光形成轨迹，而静止的物体保持清晰。
英文内容: long exposure shot style . Moving objects appear blurred or streaked due to the long exposure time, such as flowing water looking smooth or car lights creating trails, while stationary objects remain sharp

内容: 短曝光拍摄风格。图像捕捉到瞬间时刻，移动物体的模糊程度最小，从而清晰地呈现出静止和移动元素的细节。
英文内容: short exposure shot style . The image captures a moment in time with minimal blurring of moving objects, resulting in sharp and clear details of both stationary and moving elements

内容: 背景虚化风格。图像中焦外区域的美丽模糊、圆形或多边形形状，通常来自镜头光圈，创造出令人愉悦的背景模糊效果。
英文内容: bokeh style . Beautifully blurred, circular or polygonal shapes in the out - of - focus areas of the image, typically from the aperture of a lens, creating a pleasing background blur

内容: 红蓝立体摄影风格。通过明显的红色-青色或其他红蓝立体色分离，当使用适当的立体眼镜观看时，可在前景和背景元素之间创建清晰的深度感，产生生动的3D效果。
英文内容: anaglyph 3d photography style . Distinct red - cyan or other anaglyph color separation, creating a vivid 3D effect when viewed with proper glasses, clear depth perception between foreground and background elements

内容: 景深风格。聚焦主体与模糊的前景或背景之间有明显的分离，强调主体，并在图像中营造出三维空间感
英文内容: depth of field style . A clear separation between the focused subject and the blurred foreground or background, emphasizing the subject and creating a sense of three - dimensional space in the image

标题: 去饱和的脏污滤镜拍摄
内容: 褪色的脏旧滤镜拍摄风格。一种饱和度低的色彩配色方案，带有脏污、粗糙的质感，可能显示出磨损、划痕或年代感，赋予图像粗糙和原始的外观。
英文内容: desaturated grunge filter shot style . A desaturated color palette with a grungy, dirty texture, perhaps showing signs of wear, scratches, or age, giving the image a rough and raw look

内容: 高速液体拍摄风格。液体在运动中被捕获，展示了详细的水滴、飞溅或水流，由于高速摄影而被冻结在时间中，液体形状和运动的细节清晰可见。
英文内容: high - speed liquid shot style . Liquid captured in mid - motion, showing detailed droplets, splashes, or streams, frozen in time due to high - speed photography, with sharp details of the liquid's shape and movement

内容: LOMO效果拍摄风格。高对比度色彩、暗角（画面角落变暗）以及轻微的扭曲或梦幻般的视觉效果，这是Lomo相机的特征，赋予图像独特的艺术感。
英文内容: lomo effect shot style . High - contrast colors, vignetting (darkening of the corners), and a slightly distorted or dreamy look, characteristic of Lomo cameras, giving the image a unique and artistic feel

内容: 红外滤镜拍摄风格。图像具有独特的红外外观，由于红外滤镜的作用，色彩会发生独特的变化，如树叶呈现出亮白色或其他物体因红外滤镜效果而呈现出不寻常的颜色表现。
英文内容: infrared filter shot style . The image has a distinct infrared - look, with unique color shifts, such as foliage appearing bright white or other objects having unusual color representations due to the infrared filter

内容: 太阳化拍摄风格。图像在高对比区域具有特征性的色调反转，部分区域呈现类似负片的效果，通常能创造出独特和艺术的外观。
英文内容: solarized shot style . The image has a characteristic reversal of tones in the high - contrast areas, with a partial negative - like appearance, often creating a unique and artistic look

内容: 辉光效果风格。在明亮的对象或光源周围产生柔和、发光的光晕，模拟花朵绽放的效果，为图像增添梦幻和超凡的质感。
英文内容: bloom effect style . Soft, glowing halos around bright objects or light sources, simulating a blooming flower - like effect, adding a dreamy and ethereal quality to the image

内容: 中等景深风格。图像中有一部分是清晰的，前景和背景的模糊过渡柔和，平衡了主题及其周围环境的焦点。
英文内容: medium depth of field style . A moderate amount of the image is in focus, with a soft transition to the blurred foreground and background, balancing the focus between the subject and its surroundings

内容: 选择性上色风格。图像中只有特定部分是彩色的，其余部分则为黑白，突出彩色元素，创造出强烈的视觉对比。
英文内容: selective color style . Only certain parts of the image are in color while the rest is in black and white, drawing attention to the colored elements and creating a strong visual contrast

内容: 渐变效果风格。两种或更多颜色之间的平滑过渡，创建和谐且视觉上吸引人的渐变效果，可以是线性、径向或其他图案。
英文内容: gradient effect style . A smooth transition between two or more colors, creating a harmonious and visually appealing gradient, which can be linear, radial, or in other patterns

内容: 双重曝光拍摄风格。两个或更多的图像相互叠加，创造出元素的独特混合，两个曝光以艺术的方式相互作用和融合。
英文内容: double exposure shot style . Two or more images superimposed on each other, creating a unique blend of elements, with the two exposures interacting and merging in an artistic way

内容: 特艺风格。鲜艳、饱和、对比度高的颜色，类似于经典特艺电影的外观，使图像视觉上引人注目且充满活力
英文内容: technicolor shot style . Vivid, saturated, and highly contrasted colors, similar to the look of classic Technicolor films, making the image visually striking and vibrant

内容: 网点效果风格。图像由不同大小和密度的微小点组成，类似于网点印刷技术，赋予其经典的印刷外观。
英文内容: halftone effect style . The image is composed of tiny dots of different sizes and densities, similar to the halftone printing technique, giving it a classic, printed - look appearance

内容: 银版照相风格。一种具有高度细节、单色且带有金属光泽的图像，具有银版照相摄影的特点，通常带有轻微的颗粒质感，给人一种历史真实感
英文内容: daguerrotype shot style . A highly detailed, monochromatic image with a metallic sheen, characteristic of daguerrotype photography, often with a slightly grainy texture and a sense of historical authenticity

内容: 中性密度滤镜拍摄风格。图像整体亮度降低，允许在明亮条件下进行更长时间的曝光，通常会使移动元素如水或云呈现出平滑的外观。
英文内容: neutral density filters shot style . The image has a reduced overall brightness, allowing for longer exposure times in bright conditions, often resulting in a smooth look for moving elements like water or clouds
